# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2
translate spanish d8a_85b112b5:

    # "{color=#eaf50e}This next event will progress the plot and make [S] unavailable for some time. Do you wish to proceed?"
    "{color=#eaf50e}Este próximo acontecimiento hará avanzar la trama y hará que [S] no esté disponible durante algún tiempo. ¿Deseas continuar?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:12
translate spanish d8a_155d151e:

    # Z "[S] is training with Mandisa for the last time."
    Z "[S] se entrena con Mandisa por última vez."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:13
translate spanish d8a_4f48844c:

    # Z "I should prepare everything for when she comes back."
    Z "Debería preparar todo para cuando ella vuelva."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:22
translate spanish d8a_c4b24531:

    # Ma "Stay focused, [S]."
    Ma "Mantén la concentración, [S]."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:25
translate spanish d8a_e947adf8:

    # Ma "Remember: there are no safe places in a Zone, you need to be alert at all times."
    Ma "Recuerda: no hay lugares seguros en una Zona, tienes que estar alerta en todo momento."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:28
translate spanish d8a_0df706f5:

    # Ma "If you don't feel ready, you can always wait for the next one to appear."
    Ma "Si no te sientes preparada, siempre puedes esperar a que aparezca el siguiente."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:31
translate spanish d8a_700dea3b:

    # S "I have trained long enough..."
    S "He entrenado lo suficiente..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:34
translate spanish d8a_79153329:

    # Ma "And that means what exactly?"
    Ma "¿Y eso qué significa exactamente?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:35
translate spanish d8a_562ada03:

    # Ma "Some people spend a lifetime to understand how a Zone works."
    Ma "Algunas personas pasan toda una vida para entender cómo funciona una Zona."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:36
translate spanish d8a_d3e4deaa:

    # Ma "What makes you ready, [S]?!"
    Ma "¡¿Qué te hace estar preparada, [S]?!"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:37
translate spanish d8a_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:43
translate spanish d8a_2692b048:

    # S "I don't need to understand how they work, Lady Mandisa."
    S "No necesito entender cómo funcionan, Lady Mandisa."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:44
translate spanish d8a_9a01d9c1:

    # S "To put it in your words:"
    S "Para decirlo con tus palabras:"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:45
translate spanish d8a_cecac08f:

    # S "\"We cannot truly conquer a Zone, so we must act on our instincts.\""
    S "\"No podemos conquistar de verdad una Zona, así que debemos actuar según nuestros instintos.\""

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:48
translate spanish d8a_e106da53:

    # Ma "So you remember..."
    Ma "Así que lo recuerdas..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:49
translate spanish d8a_1a5e43dc:

    # Ma "It has been a long time since I said that to you."
    Ma "Hace mucho tiempo que no te decía eso."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:52
translate spanish d8a_23b2589a:

    # S "I remember. You also told me you were going to train my instincts."
    S "Lo recuerdo. También me dijiste que ibas a entrenar mis instintos."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:53
translate spanish d8a_7c0793ce:

    # S "This is it."
    S "Esto es todo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:54
translate spanish d8a_6b7a45e8:

    # S "I think I am ready for it; as ready as I will ever be."
    S "Creo que estoy preparada para ello; tan preparada como jamás he estado."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:57
translate spanish d8a_f7766cab:

    # Ma "And you are, [S]."
    Ma "Y así es, [S]."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:58
translate spanish d8a_30ebc1a5:

    # Ma "You have been an excellent student, and I am proud of you."
    Ma "Has sido una excelente estudiante, y estoy orgullosa de ti."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:61
translate spanish d8a_143d5d98:

    # S "Thank you, Lady Mandisa."
    S "Gracias, Lady Mandisa."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:64
translate spanish d8a_fa127112:

    # Ma "Before you go, let me remind you of a few things."
    Ma "Antes de que te vayas, déjame recordarte algunas cosas."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:67
translate spanish d8a_a8a46294:

    # Ma "I have trained you for many years, since you were young."
    Ma "Te he entrenado durante muchos años, desde que eras joven."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:68
translate spanish d8a_3d5147cb:

    # Ma "You fight well, you are intelligent, and I am confident that you will know when to take a fight and when to retreat."
    Ma "Peleas bien, eres inteligente, y confío en que sabrás cuándo aceptar una pelea y cuándo retirarte."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:71
translate spanish d8a_9938b397:

    # Ma "But you also have grown up to be an attractive young woman."
    Ma "Pero también has crecido hasta convertirte en una joven atractiva."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:72
translate spanish d8a_60f16287:

    # Ma "The men and women you will face will not be oblivious of that fact."
    Ma "Los hombres y mujeres a los que te enfrentarás no serán ajenos a este hecho."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:73
translate spanish d8a_0866a3fd:

    # Ma "I must remind you that in this world, all the spoils go to the victor, and that submission in defeat is a given."
    Ma "Debo recordarte que en este mundo, todo el botín es para el vencedor, y que la sumisión en la derrota es un hecho."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:76
translate spanish d8a_6d17a86b:

    # Ma "It is good that you're not shy about your looks, but it is a double edged sword. You can use it to your advantage, as a tool of distraction."
    Ma "Es bueno que no seas tímida con tu aspecto, pero es un arma de doble filo. Puedes utilizarla en tu beneficio, como herramienta de distracción."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:77
translate spanish d8a_7cb0cbd6:

    # Ma "...but there will be times where your beauty will be an added motivation for your opponents."
    Ma "... pero habrá momentos en los que tu belleza será una motivación añadida para tus oponentes."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:78
translate spanish d8a_11331a9f:

    # Ma "Conquering you will taste better to them than defeating a random fighter."
    Ma "Conquistarte les sabrá mejor que derrotar a un luchador cualquiera."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:79
translate spanish d8a_d9be5be6:

    # Ma "Your father made that mistake too, once."
    Ma "Tu padre también cometió ese error, una vez."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:82
translate spanish d8a_e4acf008:

    # Ma "So don't let it come to it. If the situation demands it, let them think you are surrendering, and wait for a better opportunity to strike."
    Ma "Así que no dejes que llegue a eso. Si la situación lo requiere, deja que piensen que te estás rindiendo, y espera una mejor oportunidad para atacar."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:85
translate spanish d8a_a61fe84e:

    # Ma "Should they see the opportunity, they will jump at the chance of winning a trophy, and not just surviving a fight."
    Ma "Si ven la oportunidad, saltarán ante la posibilidad de ganar un trofeo, y no sólo de sobrevivir a una pelea."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:86
translate spanish d8a_c2eac11a:

    # S "I will keep that in mind, thank you."
    S "Lo tendré en cuenta, gracias."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:89
translate spanish d8a_bfdbc53b:

    # Ma "Good, but there is one last, important thing you need to remember."
    Ma "Bien, pero hay una última cosa importante que debes recordar."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:92
translate spanish d8a_2ac2d8c6:

    # Ma "The most dangerous threats you will encounter in the Zone are those you can neither fight nor kill. Know when to run, and that there is no shame in it."
    Ma "Las amenazas más peligrosas que encontrarás en la Zona son las que no puedes combatir ni matar. Saber cuándo debes huir, y que no hay que avergonzarse de ello."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:93
translate spanish d8a_cd740910:

    # Ma "Best of luck, [S]. I will see you again."
    Ma "Mucha suerte, [S]. Nos veremos de nuevo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:96
translate spanish d8a_fe52059f:

    # S "Goodbye, Lady Mandisa. Thank you for everything."
    S "Adiós, Lady Mandisa. Gracias por todo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:99
translate spanish d8a_f9fc005f:

    # "As [S] is heading home, you and [W] are preparing the equipment needed."
    "Mientras [S] se dirige a casa, tú y [W] preparáis el equipo necesario."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:103
translate spanish d8a20_0ca4bda5:

    # "Unexpectedly, Igor comes over to help with your preparations."
    "Inesperadamente, Igor se acerca para ayudarte con tus preparativos."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:104
translate spanish d8a20_d70a06e9:

    # "As you describe the route you intend to take, he reveals to you the existence of an oasis that happens to be very close to the new zone."
    "Mientras le describes la ruta que pretendes seguir, te revela la existencia de un oasis que resulta estar muy cerca de la nueva zona."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:105
translate spanish d8a20_9d08f363:

    # "It's a trading post, he says, and considered neutral ground by all who visit it."
    "Es un puesto comercial, dice, y es considerado terreno neutral por todos los que lo visitan."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:108
translate spanish d8a20_960ee8f2:

    # A "That's a lot of stuff..."
    A "Son muchas cosas..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:111
translate spanish d8a20_ae9678a1:

    # W "And it is all needed."
    W "Y todo es necesario."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:114
translate spanish d8a20_16c82a77:

    # W "You never know what will happen, so you have to prepare for the worst, and then some more."
    W "Nunca se sabe lo que va a pasar, así que hay que prepararse para lo peor, y algo más."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:117
translate spanish d8a20_41a553ba:

    # W "They're going to stay at an oasis overnight, so they need the tents."
    W "Van a pasar la noche en un oasis, así que necesitan las tiendas de campaña."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:118
translate spanish d8a20_1a4fa0fe:

    # W "Does [S] have everything she needs in her backpack?"
    W "¿Tiene [S] todo lo que necesita en su mochila?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:121
translate spanish d8a20_14fc79a1:

    # Z "She does. I thought of all the necessary gear."
    Z "Lo tiene. He pensado en todo el equipo necesario."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:122
translate spanish d8a20_f89097fc:

    # Z "Let us hope the Zone offers a safe place to sleep though."
    Z "Pero esperemos que la Zona ofrezca un lugar seguro para dormir."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:125
translate spanish d8a20_a743a9df:

    # Ig "There is good chance she will find shelter."
    Ig "Hay muchas posibilidades de que ella encuentre refugio."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:126
translate spanish d8a20_6a53001b:

    # Ig "My caravans have avoided the place in past, more now that Zone is there."
    Ig "Mis caravanas han evitado el lugar en el pasado, más ahora que la Zona está allí."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:127
translate spanish d8a20_4e7f1755:

    # Ig "But it is industrial area, should offer some safe corners."
    Ig "Pero es zona industrial, debe ofrecer algunos rincones seguros."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:128
translate spanish d8a20_34e541fd:

    # Ig "And if you rest at oasis, you have short way to Zone in morning."
    Ig "Y si descansas en el 'oasis', tendrás un camino corto a la Zona por la mañana."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:131
translate spanish d8a20_6af8e0cf:

    # W "Are you sure it's safe there, Igor?"
    W "¿Estás seguro de que no allí hay peligro, Igor?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:132
translate spanish d8a20_d2e0fccf:

    # W "What if there are bandits in the oasis?"
    W "¿Y si hay bandidos en el oasis?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:135
translate spanish d8a20_da81752e:

    # Ig "I assure you, Lady [W], Oasis is one of safest places in these lands."
    Ig "Se lo aseguro, Señora [W], que el\"Oasis' es uno de los lugares más seguros de estas tierras."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:136
translate spanish d8a20_2ebeb828:

    # Ig "People will welcome them; hospitality law applies to all, in desert."
    Ig "La gente les acogerá; la ley de la hospitalidad se aplica a todos, en el desierto."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:138
translate spanish d8a20_020f2cc8:

    # S "What's going on here?"
    S "¿Qué pasa aquí?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:141
translate spanish d8a20_1f671afb:

    # S "I didn't know I was moving out?"
    S "No sabía que me iba a mudar..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:145
translate spanish d8a20_e67e52f4:

    # A "There you are, [S]!"
    A "¡Aquí estás, [S]!"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:148
translate spanish d8a20_6a0c478b:

    # A "[persistent.dad!c] and everybody else has been preparing for your journey for hours!"
    A "[persistent.dad!c] y todos los demás han estado preparando tu viaje durante horas."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:151
translate spanish d8a20_9f62ae0c:

    # S "And what do you do up there, [A]?"
    S "¿Y tú qué haces ahí arriba, [A]?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:152
translate spanish d8a20_f1eb0a6e:

    # S "It's just a trip, I will be back in a week or so."
    S "Es sólo un viaje, volveré en una semana más o menos."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:155
translate spanish d8a20_06ccf6d6:

    # S "[persistent.dad!c], I don't know why everyone is here, but I am here now, we can leave."
    S "[persistent.dad!c], no sé por qué todo el mundo está aquí, pero yo ya estoy aquí, podemos irnos."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:158
translate spanish d8a20_73a167b6:

    # Z "Loading everything took a while; no need to rush things now."
    Z "Cargar todo ha llevado un tiempo; no hay que precipitarse ahora."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:161
translate spanish d8a20_179990d6:

    # S "Igor, you're here too? Can I ask what for?"
    S "Igor, ¿tú también estás aquí? ¿Puedo preguntar para qué?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:164
translate spanish d8a20_e6629eaf:

    # Ig "I heard you leave soon, so I was curious if I can help."
    Ig "He oído que te ibas pronto, así que tenía curiosidad por saber si podía ayudar."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:165
translate spanish d8a20_9f698df8:

    # Ig "So I discussed route with your [persistent.dad]."
    Ig "Así que analicé la ruta con tu [persistent.dad]."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:168
translate spanish d8a20_d1d93c13:

    # S "So that means you are done, right?"
    S "Eso significa que habéis terminado, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:169
translate spanish d8a20_143ab56c:

    # S "Do you have anything else to discuss?"
    S "¿Tenéis algo más que discutir?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:172
translate spanish d8a20_120ace71:

    # Ig "No, I do not."
    Ig "No, no lo creo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:175
translate spanish d8a20_770e33b5:

    # Ig "..."
    Ig "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:181
translate spanish d8a20_69663a56:

    # "With a nod of appreciation and a little frown at [S]'s attitude, you thank your friend for his help."
    "Con un gesto de agradecimiento y frunciendo un poco el ceño ante la actitud de [S], agradeces a tu amigo su ayuda."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:184
translate spanish d8a20_ed8eb3e0:

    # Ig "Best wishes on your journey, Lady [S]. I know this is hard time coming."
    Ig "Mis mejores deseos en tu viaje, Señorita [S]. Sé que es un momento difícil."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:187
translate spanish d8a20_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:190
translate spanish d8a20_2865adc5:

    # S "I am ready to head out."
    S "Estoy lista para salir."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:193
translate spanish d8a20_bd13b505:

    # S "Is my backpack in there too?"
    S "¿Mi mochila también está ahí?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:194
translate spanish d8a20_60d17cae:

    # W "[S]..."
    W "[S]..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:197
translate spanish d8a20_c1baf612:

    # S "[persistent.mom!c], I think you helped enough."
    S "[persistent.mom!c], creo que ya has ayudado lo suficiente."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:200
translate spanish d8a20_2350e2f3:

    # S "So, are we ready now or what?"
    S "Así que, ¿ya estamos listos o qué?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:203
translate spanish d8a20_fab2b885:

    # W "[S], enough!!!"
    W "[S], ¡¡¡basta!!!"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:204
translate spanish d8a20_971a98df_1:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:207
translate spanish d8a20_c2c9cc07:

    # W "..."
    W "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:210
translate spanish d8a20_6b9131cc:

    # W "Look at me..."
    W "Mírame..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:213
translate spanish d8a20_c2c9cc07_1:

    # W "..."
    W "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:216
translate spanish d8a20_2a470c7c:

    # "She moves in closer..."
    "Ella se acerca más..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:219
translate spanish d8a20_623375dd:

    # W "You will tell me what your problem is, and you will do it now!"
    W "Me dirás cuál es tu problema, ¡y lo harás ahora!"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:222
translate spanish d8a20_72cea523:

    # S "It's not me who has a problem."
    S "No soy yo quien tiene un problema."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:223
translate spanish d8a20_2c556c26:

    # S "I just want to go on this mission, and everyone here is treating it like I'm moving out or going to die."
    S "Sólo quiero irme a esta misión, y todo el mundo aquí lo trata como si me fuera a mudar o me fuera a morir."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:226
translate spanish d8a20_6697a05e:

    # W "Do you think [A] wants her sister to move out?!"
    W "¡¿Crees que [A] quiere que su hermana se mude?!"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:227
translate spanish d8a20_c2b4c895:

    # W "And do you think that is why Igor took the time to try to help out, because he doesn't want to see you anymore?!"
    W "¡¿Y crees que por eso Igor se ha tomado la molestia de intentar ayudar, porque no quiere verte más?!"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:228
translate spanish d8a20_934f6c9e:

    # W "Is that how you treat those who help you, by lashing out? Speak to me, my girl."
    W "¿Es así como tratas a los que te ayudan, arremetiendo contra ellos? Dime, mi niña."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:231
translate spanish d8a20_229c4f43:

    # S "No, [persistent.mom]..."
    S "No, [persistent.mom]..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:232
translate spanish d8a20_25d3beab:

    # W "Then what is it?!"
    W "Entonces, ¿qué es?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:235
translate spanish d8a20_54656cb2:

    # S "I don't know, [persistent.mom]."
    S "No lo sé, [persistent.mom]."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:236
translate spanish d8a20_6e373c65:

    # S "I'm sorry, I just don't want all this attention."
    S "Lo siento, no quiero toda esta atención."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:237
translate spanish d8a20_46c4dfe7:

    # S "I want to go and focus, but having everyone fussing around me..."
    S "Quiero ir y concentrarme, pero tener a todo el mundo alborotando a mi alrededor..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:240
translate spanish d8a20_30d5576f:

    # S "We are not saying goodbye, so let's not treat it like a last family gathering."
    S "No nos estamos despidiendo, así que no lo tratemos como una última reunión familiar."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:241
translate spanish d8a20_d52bf8ad:

    # S "I will be gone a few days, weeks maybe, and I know the risks, but please let me go quietly."
    S "Estaré fuera unos días, semanas quizás, y conozco los riesgos, pero por favor, dejadme ir tranquilamente."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:244
translate spanish d8a20_60d17cae_1:

    # W "[S]..."
    W "[S]..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:245
translate spanish d8a20_971a98df_2:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:248
translate spanish d8a20_b69ec9ae:

    # W "Baby, come here."
    W "Nena, ven aquí."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:251
translate spanish d8a20_929b1977:

    # Ww "All will be good, this should not be a sad day."
    Ww "Todo irá bien, no debería ser un día triste."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:252
translate spanish d8a20_50488d3b:

    # Ww "And you are right; you will come back soon."
    Ww "Y tienes razón; volverás pronto."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:253
translate spanish d8a20_fb2083d9:

    # Ww "We prepared everything, so, are you ready to head out?"
    Ww "Lo hemos preparado todo, así que, ¿estás lista para salir?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:256
translate spanish d8a20_7ff9fc50:

    # S "Mhm..."
    S "Mhm..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:259
translate spanish d8a20_f1e9b688:

    # "A few minutes later..."
    "Unos minutos más tarde..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:262
translate spanish d8a20_cad53cb7:

    # A "I know you got this, [S]."
    A "Sé que lo entiendes, [S]."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:263
translate spanish d8a20_ddf056f4:

    # A "Once you're back, you have to tell me everything."
    A "Cuando vuelvas, tendrás que contarme todo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:266
translate spanish d8a20_2d9af70c:

    # S "Thank you, [A]. And I will."
    S "Gracias, [A]. Y lo haré."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:267
translate spanish d8a20_11b13037:

    # S "I know I have not always treated you well."
    S "Sé que no siempre te he tratado bien."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:268
translate spanish d8a20_8928eab4:

    # S "We should do more things together once I'm back."
    S "Deberíamos hacer más cosas juntas una vez que haya vuelto."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:271
translate spanish d8a20_5a072d4c:

    # A "That would be cool. Let's do that!"
    A "Eso sería genial. Hagámoslo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:274
translate spanish d8a20_d6534d48:

    # W "So... time to go?"
    W "Así que... ¿es hora de irse?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:278
translate spanish d8a20_179900a8:

    # "You head out into the desert together."
    "Salís juntos al desierto."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:279
translate spanish d8a20_b972c32a:

    # "It soon becomes obvious that [S] is understandably nervous. Thinking ahead, you hope that spending a last night together before the challenge really starts will give her time to compose her mind."
    "Pronto se hace evidente que [S] está comprensiblemente nerviosa. Pensando en el futuro, esperas que pasar una última noche juntos antes de que comience realmente el desafío le dé tiempo para componer su mente."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:283
translate spanish d8a20_e36d8875:

    # Z "If Igor is correct, we shouldn't be far away now."
    Z "Si Igor está en lo cierto, ahora no deberíamos estar muy lejos."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:284
translate spanish d8a20_5e442042:

    # Z "Who knows, maybe the place will be empty, maybe not."
    Z "Quién sabe, tal vez el lugar esté vacío, tal vez no."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:285
translate spanish d8a20_688a200b:

    # Z "Based on his description, there are worse places to spend the night."
    Z "Según su descripción, hay lugares peores para pasar la noche."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:288
translate spanish d8a20_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:291
translate spanish d8a20_d0f0679e:

    # Z "Maybe, if we find someone, they will have interesting stories to tell. You never know."
    Z "Tal vez, si encontramos a alguien, tenga historias interesantes que contar. Nunca se sabe."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:292
translate spanish d8a20_eb40876a:

    # Z "If they travel this route often, they've maybe seen others heading there too. That would be good to know in advance."
    Z "Si viajan a menudo por esta ruta, tal vez hayan visto a otros dirigirse hacia allí también. Sería bueno saberlo de antemano."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:293
translate spanish d8a20_744722a4:

    # Z "Who knows, maybe we will even meet a Stalker from the outside."
    Z "Quién sabe, tal vez nos encontremos con un Acechador del exterior."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:299
translate spanish d8a20_5ab3574d_1:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:300
translate spanish d8a20_9e4a1b64:

    # Z "Everything will work out, I promise."
    Z "Todo se solucionará, te lo prometo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:303
translate spanish d8a20_971a98df_3:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:306
translate spanish d8a20_3c232f47:

    # Z "I know it will."
    Z "Sé que lo hará."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:317
translate spanish d8a20_d95964c4:

    # Z "...and here we are.{p=4} {nw}"
    Z "... y aquí estamos.{p=4} {nw}"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:321
translate spanish d8a20_ede421d0:

    # Z "The Zone is really not far from here.{p=4} {nw}"
    Z "La Zona no está realmente lejos de aquí.{p=4} {nw}"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:324
translate spanish d8a20_a705758d:

    # Z "Do you want to set up the camp?{p=4} {nw}"
    Z "¿Quieres montar el campamento?{p=4} {nw}"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:325
translate spanish d8a20_42a1dca9:

    # S "Okay...{p=3} {nw}"
    S "Bueno...{p=3} {nw}"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:355
translate spanish d8a20_e90a0737:

    # C2 "...{p=1.5} {nw}"
    C2 "... {p=1.5} {nw}"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:358
translate spanish d8a20_1b0297f5:

    # C2 "Hey, Heka; you think those folks could use some company?{p=4} {nw}"
    C2 "Ey, Heka; ¿crees que a esa gente le vendría bien algo de compañía? {p=4} {nw}"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:361
translate spanish d8a20_0399e69a:

    # C3 "I suppose. Ask them!{p=3} {nw}"
    C3 "Supongo que sí. ¡Pregúntales! {p=3} {nw}"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:364
translate spanish d8a20_d03d3a6e:

    # C2 "Hey! You two!{p=3} {nw}"
    C2 "¡Ey! ¡Vosotros! {p=3} {nw}"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:365
translate spanish d8a20_53dac914:

    # C2 "You look a bit lost over there, why don't you join us for the evening?{p=4.5} {nw}"
    C2 "Pareceis un poco perdidos por ahí, ¿por qué no os unís a nosotros por la noche?{p=4.5} {nw}"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:369
translate spanish d8a20_08442159:

    # Z "What do you think? I say it won't hurt to be friendly.{p=4} {nw}"
    Z "¿Qué opinas? Yo digo que no nos vendrá mal ser amables.{p=4} {nw}"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:372
translate spanish d8a20_3c29c16e:

    # Z "Come, let's pay them a visit.{p=4} {nw}"
    Z "Ven, vamos a hacerles una visita.{p=4} {nw}"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:376
translate spanish d8a20_4cb164dc:

    # "You and [S] introduce yourselves to the other travellers in the oasis. You settle down and break bread together."
    "Tú y [S] os presentáis a los demás viajeros del oasis. Os acomodáis y compartís el pan."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:377
translate spanish d8a20_63f7f257:

    # "As Igor predicted, they turn out to be traders leading a small caravan through the desert..."
    "Como predijo Igor, resultan ser comerciantes que conducen una pequeña caravana por el desierto..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:381
translate spanish d8a20_3ddcc2c8:

    # He "...yeah, your friend Igor was right, this has long been a neutral place, where people come together to shake some of the sand off their boots, in peace."
    He "... sí, tu amigo Igor tenía razón, este ha sido durante mucho tiempo un lugar neutral, donde la gente se reúne para sacudirse un poco de arena de las botas, en paz."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:384
translate spanish d8a20_71020ae0:

    # He "Eventually we all decided to set up a permanent camp here."
    He "Finalmente, todos decidimos establecer un campamento permanente aquí."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:385
translate spanish d8a20_58914b86:

    # He "Caravans go in and out, and so far the agreement stands, even with other, less peaceful, folk."
    He "Las caravanas van y vienen, y hasta ahora el acuerdo se mantiene, incluso con gente menos pacífica."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:388
translate spanish d8a20_b1a42e96:

    # S "That's pretty cool."
    S "Está muy bien."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:391
translate spanish d8a20_f0a85a2a:

    # He "Eva and I travel this route quite frequently, and we really can't complain."
    He "Eva y yo recorremos esta ruta con bastante frecuencia, y realmente no podemos quejarnos."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:392
translate spanish d8a20_169640c1:

    # He "Granted, now that that unsettling Zone appeared, I expect fewer people to come this way..."
    He "Por supuesto, ahora que ha aparecido la Zona Inquietante, supongo que vendrá menos gente por aquí..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:393
translate spanish d8a20_527a24bc:

    # He "...which might actually work in favour of those who do."
    He "... lo cual podría ser a favor de los que sí vengan."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:394
translate spanish d8a20_188886e7:

    # He "And with two Stalkers in my camp, I'm definitely not going to worry for our safety tonight."
    He "Y con dos Acechadores en mi campamento, definitivamente no voy a preocuparme por nuestra seguridad, esta noche."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:397
translate spanish d8a20_fd369ce3:

    # Jaz "So, I'm guessing you two are going to head out there tomorrow morning?"
    Jaz "Supongo que vosotros dos os dirigiréis allí mañana por la mañana."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:400
translate spanish d8a20_a695ecf8:

    # S "Yeah, sort of..."
    S "Sí, más o menos..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:401
translate spanish d8a20_392c4672:

    # S "I will be the only one going."
    S "Yo seré la única que vaya."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:404
translate spanish d8a20_1ac7e868:

    # Jaz "Oh..."
    Jaz "Oh..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:405
translate spanish d8a20_9d66925d:

    # Jaz "But... I don't understand?"
    Jaz "Pero... No entiendo..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:408
translate spanish d8a20_9a061581:

    # Ev "It's a long standing tradition, in Zeta, for new Stalkers to face their first Zone on their own."
    Ev "Es una tradición muy antigua, en Zeta, que los nuevos Acechadores se enfrenten a su primera Zona por sí mismos."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:411
translate spanish d8a20_8a5e7d0c:

    # Ev "I've only heard stories, but they say that even though the first visit is very dangerous to an inexperienced Stalker, it's also the most personal one, never to be forgotten."
    Ev "Sólo he oído historias, pero dicen que aunque la primera visita es muy peligrosa para un Acechador inexperto, también es la más personal, que nunca se olvida."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:414
translate spanish d8a20_e83e51e6:

    # He "Now, what do you think, [persistent.player_name]? I say we try to put the fears of tomorrow out of our minds and enjoy the evening."
    He "Ahora, ¿qué opinas, [persistent.player_name]? Yo digo que tratemos de apartar de nuestras mentes los temores de mañana y disfrutemos de la velada."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:417
translate spanish d8a20_14eab133:

    # Z "I'm not against that, what do you have in mind?"
    Z "No estoy en contra de eso, ¿qué tienes en mente?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:420
translate spanish d8a20_5868bfe4:

    # He "Oh, I know something we can do."
    He "Oh, sé algo que podemos hacer."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:423
translate spanish d8a20_8caaea1c:

    # Jaz "I hope you'll go easy on yourself this time, [He]."
    Jaz "Espero que esta vez vayas con calma contigo mismo, [He]."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:427
translate spanish d8a20_33a46fdf:

    # "Some time later..."
    "Pasado un tiempo..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:431
translate spanish d8a20_b4e1e922:

    # Jaz "..."
    Jaz "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:432
translate spanish d8a20_e560d4e8:

    # Jaz "...you have gone too far, again..."
    Jaz "... te has pasado, otra vez..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:433
translate spanish d8a20_dd66a2e8:

    # Z "...Is he always this generous, when he loads the pipe?"
    Z "... ¿El siempre es tan generoso cuando carga la pipa?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:434
translate spanish d8a20_0773d3e2:

    # Jaz "Yep... yep."
    Jaz "Síp... síp."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:437
translate spanish d8a20_50be4d48:

    # Jaz "That last one hit me in a different way."
    Jaz "Esta última me golpeó de una manera diferente."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:440
translate spanish d8a20_2d31aea7:

    # He "You've got to enjoy the moment, Jazmin..."
    He "Tienes que disfrutar del momento, Jazmin..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:441
translate spanish d8a20_29b456da:

    # He "...damn, I'm good."
    He "... maldita sea, estoy bien."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:444
translate spanish d8a20_aeed1f6f:

    # Zt "Whoa..."
    Zt "Guauu..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:447
translate spanish d8a20_10fb7035:

    # Zt "That was strong stuff..."
    Zt "Esto fue algo fuerte..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:450
translate spanish d8a20_81a6b25c:

    # Z "Hey, you okay?"
    Z "Ey, ¿estás bien?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:451
translate spanish d8a20_967f18a1:

    # Ev "{i}*chuckles*{/i} is she sleeping?"
    Ev "{i}*risilla*{/i} ¿está durmiendo?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:454
translate spanish d8a20_de92d35c:

    # Ev "Hey, [S], the evening is not over yet!"
    Ev "Ey, [S], ¡la noche aún no ha terminado!"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:455
translate spanish d8a20_1e2951f6:

    # Ev "If you're sleeping just tell us!"
    Ev "Si estás durmiendo, ¡dínoslo!"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:461
translate spanish d8a20_076d5732:

    # S "Mmhm..."
    S "Umhm..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:464
translate spanish d8a20_971a98df_4:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:467
translate spanish d8a20_7cd5d7f7:

    # Ev "She must've had a long day. Should we let her rest?"
    Ev "Debe haber tenido un día muy largo. ¿Debemos dejarla descansar?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:471
translate spanish d8a20_076d5732_1:

    # S "Mmhm..."
    S "Umhm..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:472
translate spanish d8a20_7cd5d7f7_1:

    # Ev "She must've had a long day. Should we let her rest?"
    Ev "Debe haber tenido un día muy largo. ¿Debemos dejarla descansar?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:475
translate spanish d8a20_e246992d:

    # S "...?"
    S "¿...?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:478
translate spanish d8a20_9f8c779c:

    # S "N-no no... I'm fine, I'm here."
    S "N-no no... estoy bien, estoy aquí."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:481
translate spanish d8a20_c52e1e94:

    # Ev "I would say I'm sorry for [He]'s doing, but I think maybe you needed that one."
    Ev "Diría que siento lo que ha hecho [He], pero creo que tal vez lo necesitabas."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:484
translate spanish d8a20_ebc5fc90:

    # He "Hey... hey... look..."
    He "Ey... ey... mira..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:487
translate spanish d8a20_60bad48a:

    # He "I didn't want to knock anyone out, okay."
    He "No quería noquear a nadie, de acuerdo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:488
translate spanish d8a20_cd70a9f9:

    # He "I may have overdone it... a little bit... again... I admit that."
    He "Puede que me haya pasado un poco... otra vez... Lo admito."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:491
translate spanish d8a20_e33c5f01:

    # Jaz "Hgrh...!"
    Jaz "¡Agrh...!"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:494
translate spanish d8a20_bf90570e:

    # Jaz "Guys..."
    Jaz "Chicos..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:497
translate spanish d8a20_22a5ea13:

    # Jaz "...as nice as this was, I should call it a night."
    Jaz "... por muy agradable que haya sido, yo debería dar por terminada la noche."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:500
translate spanish d8a20_ca4fd1b6:

    # Ev "Aww... Jazmin..."
    Ev "Ohh... Jazmin..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:501
translate spanish d8a20_8b8e5d05:

    # Ev "...I can't blame you though."
    Ev "... sin embargo, no puedo culparte."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:504
translate spanish d8a20_880ee248:

    # Jaz "It was nice meeting you two. See you back in Zeta, maybe."
    Jaz "Ha sido un placer conoceros. Quizá nos veamos en Zeta."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:505
translate spanish d8a20_295ded4a:

    # Z "Good night Jazmin, take care."
    Z "Buenas noches Jazmin, cuídate."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:508
translate spanish d8a20_f8080529:

    # "She leaves the tent..."
    "Ella se va de la tienda..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:511
translate spanish d8a20_af9c9ab5:

    # S "She seems like a nice person."
    S "Parece una persona agradable."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:514
translate spanish d8a20_be92f612:

    # Ev "Jazmin? Oh yes."
    Ev "¿Jazmín? Oh, sí."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:515
translate spanish d8a20_c3557e4d:

    # Ev "She's the nicest girl you'll ever find in these lands."
    Ev "Es la chica más simpática que encontrarás en estas tierras."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:516
translate spanish d8a20_079b8546:

    # Ev "She is not from Zeta, and you can tell."
    Ev "No es de Zeta, y se nota."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:522
translate spanish d8a20_5ab3574d_2:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:523
translate spanish d8a20_a4e1ff5e:

    # S "How so?"
    S "¿Cómo es eso?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:524
translate spanish d8a20_abcfd3b1:

    # Ev "Well, she never attempts to put herself above others... is always trying to learn something new."
    Ev "Bueno, ella nunca intenta ponerse por encima de los demás... siempre está intentando aprender algo nuevo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:525
translate spanish d8a20_eeb23076:

    # Ev "To be honest, sometimes I wonder how she survives in these harsh lands."
    Ev "Para ser sincera, a veces me pregunto cómo sobrevive en estas duras tierras."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:527
translate spanish d8a20_f4acb643:

    # S "It's an uncommon mindset, I agree."
    S "Es una mentalidad poco común, estoy de acuerdo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:529
translate spanish d8a20_357e6c2c:

    # S "Maybe people just underestimate her?"
    S "¿Quizás la gente la subestima?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:530
translate spanish d8a20_adf58d14:

    # Ev "Could be..."
    Ev "Podría ser..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:531
translate spanish d8a20_5c6eab97:

    # "You feel someone looking at you..."
    "Sientes que alguien te mira..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:534
translate spanish d8a20_5bb8ac2f:

    # Ev "..."
    Ev "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:535
translate spanish d8a20_76aa4004:

    # "Although everyone is still somewhat buzzed, her expression tells you she has something on her mind."
    "Aunque todo el mundo está todavía algo zumbado, su expresión te dice que ella tiene algo en mente."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:538
translate spanish d8a20_9d5874eb:

    # Ev "Anyway... what do you guys think of stretching your legs a little?"
    Ev "En fin... ¿qué os parece estirar un poco las piernas?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:541
translate spanish d8a20_85cfe65c:

    # He "You've had worse ideas, babe... I should consider it..."
    He "Has tenido ideas peores, nena... Debería considerarlo..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:544
translate spanish d8a20_75285e41:

    # Z "I'm going to get up for a bit, too."
    Z "Yo también me voy a levantar un poco."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:545
translate spanish d8a20_09a24c62:

    # Z "It will help me regain feeling in my legs again, I should think."
    Z "Creo que me ayudará a recuperar la sensibilidad en las piernas."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:548
translate spanish d8a20_c42f5ff1:

    # S "{i}*laughs*{/i} I think you will need them eventually, yes."
    S "{i}*risas*{/i} Creo que al final las necesitarás, sí."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:551
translate spanish d8a20_b68834fd:

    # Z "Alright, let's get up."
    Z "Muy bien, vamos a levantarnos."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:557
translate spanish d8a20_a4e1ff5e_1:

    # S "How so?"
    S "¿Cómo es eso?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:560
translate spanish d8a20_abcfd3b1_1:

    # Ev "Well, she never attempts to put herself above others... is always trying to learn something new."
    Ev "Bueno, ella nunca intenta ponerse por encima de los demás... siempre está intentando aprender algo nuevo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:561
translate spanish d8a20_a444a07b:

    # Ev "To be honest, sometimes I wonder how she survives in these lands."
    Ev "Para ser sincero, a veces me pregunto cómo sobrevive en estas tierras."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:564
translate spanish d8a20_cb94cf64:

    # S "That is very remarkable, I agree."
    S "Eso es muy notable, estoy de acuerdo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:567
translate spanish d8a20_9d5874eb_1:

    # Ev "Anyway... what do you guys think of stretching your legs a little?"
    Ev "En fin... ¿qué os parece estirar un poco las piernas?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:569
translate spanish d8a20_85cfe65c_1:

    # He "You've had worse ideas, babe... I should consider it..."
    He "Has tenido ideas peores, nena... Debería considerarlo..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:572
translate spanish d8a20_a5252200:

    # Z "Not a bad idea."
    Z "No es una mala idea."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:573
translate spanish d8a20_09a24c62_1:

    # Z "It will help me regain feeling in my legs again, I should think."
    Z "Creo que me ayudará a recuperar la sensibilidad en las piernas."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:576
translate spanish d8a20_c42f5ff1_1:

    # S "{i}*laughs*{/i} I think you will need them eventually, yes."
    S "{i}*risas*{/i} Creo que al final las necesitarás, sí."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:579
translate spanish d8a20_b68834fd_1:

    # Z "Alright, let's get up."
    Z "Muy bien, vamos a levantarnos."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:586
translate spanish d8a131_cbdd60b1:

    # "Eventually..."
    "Finalmente..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:591
translate spanish d8a131_34584994:

    # S "She's beautiful."
    S "Es preciosa."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:594
translate spanish d8a131_515acc23:

    # He "We had two more, but they were too old for the trek, so we traded them away."
    He "Teníamos dos más, pero eran demasiado viejas para el viaje, así que las cambiamos."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:595
translate spanish d8a131_199626c8:

    # He "Since then, we've been looking for an opportunity to acquire a few more."
    He "Desde entonces, hemos estado buscando una oportunidad para adquirir algunas más."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:598
translate spanish d8a131_44e3ae92:

    # He "Too many places are affected by pollution and scarcity though, which makes breeding them in sufficient numbers a challenge."
    He "Sin embargo, hay demasiados lugares afectados por la contaminación y la escasez, lo que hace que criarlas en número suficiente sea un reto."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:601
translate spanish d8a131_be77d5a5:

    # S "At least we still have the car... even though we can't use it in the city."
    S "Al menos seguimos teniendo el coche... aunque no podamos usarlo en la ciudad."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:604
translate spanish d8a131_3ea7359b:

    # He "So... how are you feeling now?"
    He "Y... ¿cómo te sientes ahora?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:605
translate spanish d8a131_b21cc233:

    # He "You looked a bit down when you arrived here."
    He "Parecías un poco decaída cuando llegaste aquí."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:606
translate spanish d8a131_cfff7372:

    # He "I hope that we took away a bit of your anxiety over tomorrow?"
    He "Espero que te hayamos quitado un poco de ansiedad por lo de mañana."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:609
translate spanish d8a131_5a430656:

    # S "Yes, thank you. I had a good time."
    S "Sí, gracias. Me lo he pasado bien."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:612
translate spanish d8a131_2a740641:

    # He "I know little about the Zones and the so called emissions that happen inside there."
    He "Sé poco sobre las Zonas y las llamadas emisiones que se producen en su interior."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:613
translate spanish d8a131_41457757:

    # He "A Stalker once told me that those moments are often preceded by signs, and identifying the signs can save your life."
    He "Un Acechador me dijo una vez que esos momentos suelen ir precedidos de señales, y que identificar las señales puede salvarte la vida."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:614
translate spanish d8a131_2957e2a0:

    # He "Maybe you knew this already. If not, I offer you this knowledge, on your journey."
    He "Quizá ya lo sabías. Si no, te ofrezco este conocimiento, en tu viaje."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:617
translate spanish d8a131_db933271:

    # S "Your gift of knowledge is appreciated. I thank you."
    S "Tu don de conocimiento es apreciado. Te lo agradezco."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:620
translate spanish d8a131_78db66db:

    # He "You are schooled in the proper ways of the desert. Your [persistent.dad] taught you well."
    He "Has sido educada en las formas propias del Desierto. Tu [persistent.dad] te ha enseñado bien."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:623
translate spanish d8a131_3682a270:

    # S "Anyway... it's not really the zone itself that worries me, to be honest."
    S "De todos modos... no es la Zona en sí lo que me preocupa, para ser sincera."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:624
translate spanish d8a131_aa820539:

    # S "I am supposed to head to the Zone with nothing else on my mind, but that's not how I feel..."
    S "Se supone que me dirijo a la Zona sin pensar en nada más, pero no es así como me siento..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:625
translate spanish d8a131_6bd33811:

    # S "...it feels that I am leaving behind unfinished things, that's all."
    S "... Parece que estoy dejando cosas inacabadas, eso es todo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:628
translate spanish d8a131_8e479db0:

    # He "I totally get that. I mean, at least I think I do."
    He "Lo entiendo perfectamente. Quiero decir, al menos creo que lo entiendo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:629
translate spanish d8a131_a133ff21:

    # He "I haven't talked to many Stalkers about their tasks, but I did have one friend..."
    He "No he hablado con muchos Acechadores sobre sus tareas, pero tenía una amiga..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:630
translate spanish d8a131_28f2d165:

    # He "She was a scavenger, you know, collecting scraps from ancient ruins and all."
    He "Era una carroñera, ya sabes, que recogía restos de ruinas antiguas y todo eso."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:633
translate spanish d8a131_768ac2ea:

    # He "She always had big plans for the future, and always kept putting them on hold, telling me she would pursue them after her next trip."
    He "Siempre tenía grandes planes para el futuro, y siempre los dejaba en suspenso, diciéndome que los llevaría a cabo después de su próximo viaje"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:636
translate spanish d8a131_45faf61d:

    # He "But one day she told me: \"This will be it. After the next big trip, I will put aside all of this and focus on the things I always wanted to do.\""
    He "Pero un día me dijo: \"Esto será todo. Después del próximo gran viaje, dejaré de lado todo esto y me centraré en las cosas que siempre he querido hacer.\""

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:639
translate spanish d8a131_051fced1:

    # He "Well... long story short, she never came back from that trip."
    He "Bueno... para abreviar, ella nunca volvió de ese viaje."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:640
translate spanish d8a131_9789f4b4:

    # He "She got ambushed by raiders, whilst exploring one of those broken down planes."
    He "Le tendieron una emboscada los asaltantes, mientras exploraba uno de esos aviones averiados."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:641
translate spanish d8a131_f0f42ac7:

    # He "Only one member of her crew made it back."
    He "Sólo un miembro de su tripulación consigió volver."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:642
translate spanish d8a131_17eb4afa:

    # He "So... everything she worked for, all those things she wanted to do, they are gone, lost in the wind."
    He "Así que... todo por lo que trabajó, todas esas cosas que quería hacer, se fueron, se perdieron en el viento."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:645
translate spanish d8a131_fae6f9b2:

    # He "Now, don't get me wrong. I'm not saying that you won't come back."
    He "No me malinterpretes. No digo que no vayas a volver."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:646
translate spanish d8a131_6ff319bb:

    # He "But if there is something you want to do or say before you head towards the unknown, my suggestion is to get that over with. Deal with those things."
    He "Pero si hay algo que quieras hacer o decir antes de dirigirte a lo desconocido, mi sugerencia es que acabes con eso. Ocúpate de esas cosas."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:649
translate spanish d8a131_d8239b06:

    # He "We must travel light, in the desert. Regrets are often a load that lies heavy on the heart."
    He "Debemos viajar ligeros, en el desierto. Los remordimientos son a menudo una carga que pesa sobre el corazón."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:652
translate spanish d8a131_38aabed4:

    # S "Thank you again, [He]. Your gift of wisdom is also appreciated. I will consider your words."
    S "Gracias de nuevo, [He]. Tu regalo de sabiduría también se aprecia. Tendré en cuenta tus palabras."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:655
translate spanish d8a131_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:659
translate spanish d8a131_26d34765:

    # Ev "So, [persistent.player_name], I'm curious. What is going on between you two?"
    Ev "Entonces, [persistent.player_name], tengo curiosidad. ¿Qué pasa entre vosotros dos?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:662
translate spanish d8a131_069428b1:

    # Z "{i}*laughs*{/i} What do you mean?"
    Z "{i}*risas*{/i} ¿Qué quieres decir?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:665
translate spanish d8a131_dfcb223a:

    # Ev "You know what I'm talking about. You and your [persistent.da]."
    Ev "Sabes de lo que estoy hablando. Tú y tu [persistent.da]."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:666
translate spanish d8a131_e5f268f6:

    # Ev "I saw the way you look at her. A woman knows these things."
    Ev "He visto cómo la miras. Una mujer sabe esas cosas."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:667
translate spanish d8a131_e4274bd4:

    # Ev "You don't seem to be the shy type, so why are you hesitating?"
    Ev "No pareces ser del tipo tímido, así que ¿por qué dudas?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:673
translate spanish d8a131_bd5ef104:

    # Z "You have seen her. She {i}is{/i} easy on the eyes."
    Z "La has visto. Ella {i}es{/i} agradable a la vista."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:674
translate spanish d8a131_23843b28:

    # Z "But she has not finished her training yet, which is why I have always made an effort to restrain myself."
    Z "Pero aun no ha terminado su entrenamiento, por eso siempre me he esforzado en contenerme."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:675
translate spanish d8a131_ffe03f96:

    # Ev "That's how it works for all Zetan Stalkers, isn't it?"
    Ev "Así es como funciona para todos los Acechadores Zetanos, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:676
translate spanish d8a131_8f3551ee:

    # Z "Yes, it usually is, for the good ones. And I like to think I am very good."
    Z "Sí, suele ser así, para los buenos. Y me gusta pensar que soy muy bueno."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:679
translate spanish d8a131_d4bf4380:

    # Ev "Well then..."
    Ev "Pues entonces..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:682
translate spanish d8a131_04d85261:

    # Ev "She has a great mentor, and an even better [persistent.dad]."
    Ev "Tiene un gran mentor, y un [persistent.dad] aún mejor."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:683
translate spanish d8a131_490848d8:

    # Ev "And I'm sure she knows that."
    Ev "Y estoy segura de que ella lo sabe."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:686
translate spanish d8a131_4e8d92d3:

    # Z "Thanks, [Ev]."
    Z "Gracias, [Ev]."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:692
translate spanish d8a131_c43e6df9:

    # Z "She's a pretty girl, but she should find her own way."
    Z "Es una chica bonita, pero debería encontrar su propio camino."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:695
translate spanish d8a131_d4bf4380_1:

    # Ev "Well then..."
    Ev "Pues entonces..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:698
translate spanish d8a131_04d85261_1:

    # Ev "She has a great mentor, and an even better [persistent.dad]."
    Ev "Tiene un gran mentor, y un [persistent.dad] aún mejor."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:699
translate spanish d8a131_490848d8_1:

    # Ev "And I'm sure she knows that."
    Ev "Y estoy segura de que ella lo sabe."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:702
translate spanish d8a131_4e8d92d3_1:

    # Z "Thanks, [Ev]."
    Z "Gracias, [Ev]."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:706
translate spanish d8a131_f3dcfbd9:

    # Ev "So, [persistent.player_name], I'm curious."
    Ev "Entonces, [persistent.player_name], tengo curiosidad."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:707
translate spanish d8a131_bb0e5488:

    # Ev "Is there anything more going on between you two?"
    Ev "¿Hay algo más entre vosotros?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:710
translate spanish d8a131_1561e0a0:

    # Z "What makes you ask?"
    Z "¿Por qué te lo preguntas?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:711
translate spanish d8a131_11e0005c:

    # Ev "Things seemed a little tense between the two of you, tonight."
    Ev "Las cosas parecían un poco tensas entre los dos, esta noche."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:714
translate spanish d8a131_016b56bb:

    # Ev "I'm just asking. She's your [persistent.da], you go on adventures together and all. Such things breed closeness."
    Ev "Sólo estoy preguntando. Ella es tu [persistent.da], vais de aventuras juntos y todo eso. Esas cosas engendran cercanía."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:715
translate spanish d8a131_8e02a7e7:

    # Ev "I'm going everywhere with [He], and I could never imagine not sharing my bed with him."
    Ev "Yo voy a todas partes con [He], y nunca podría imaginarme no compartir mi cama con él."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:716
translate spanish d8a131_854ac689:

    # Ev "You seem confident enough to have no problem getting along with girls?"
    Ev "Pareces lo suficientemente seguro de ti mismo como para no tener problemas para llevarte bien con las chicas."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:717
translate spanish d8a131_77afea9f:

    # Z "{i}*laughs*{/i} Not a bad guess."
    Z "{i}*risas*{/i} No es una mala suposición."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:718
translate spanish d8a131_2ac157b6:

    # Ev "See, I knew it. So what's the story?"
    Ev "Ves, lo sabía. Entonces, ¿cuál es la historia?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:721
translate spanish d8a131_fbda52fb:

    # Ev "Looking at her, she must've been the most popular girl in school."
    Ev "Mirándola, debía ser la chica más popular de la escuela."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:722
translate spanish d8a131_59d00861:

    # Ev "Are you not interested? That's not what I thought I would see in a Zetan Stalker, of all people."
    Ev "¿No te interesa? Eso no es lo que pensé que vería en un Acechador Zetano, de todas las personas."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:727
translate spanish d8a131_c1fec382:

    # Z "Of course I am interested, but we have focused on her training before all else, until today."
    Z "Por supuesto que me interesa, pero nos hemos centrado en su formación antes que nada, hasta hoy."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:729
translate spanish d8a131_fb3cc4d0:

    # Z "That's what I've promised myself since she told me she wanted to follow in my footsteps."
    Z "Eso es lo que me he prometido desde que me dijo que quería seguir mis pasos."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:731
translate spanish d8a131_9049fb28:

    # Z "That's what I've promised myself since the day we adopted her, just like my mentor did for me."
    Z "Eso es lo que me he prometido desde el día en que la adoptamos, igual que mi mentor hizo por mí."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:732
translate spanish d8a131_ffe03f96_1:

    # Ev "That's how it works for all Zetan Stalkers, isn't it?"
    Ev "Así es como funciona para todos los Acechadores Zetanos, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:733
translate spanish d8a131_7320ecbe:

    # Z "Yes."
    Z "Sí."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:736
translate spanish d8a131_27543ca6:

    # Ev "And what if she wanted more from you too?"
    Ev "¿Y si ella también quisiera más de ti?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:740
translate spanish d8a131_3db440a3:

    # Z "We will talk about it, eventually."
    Z "Hablaremos de ello, al final."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:743
translate spanish d8a131_d4bf4380_2:

    # Ev "Well then..."
    Ev "Pues entonces..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:746
translate spanish d8a131_04d85261_2:

    # Ev "She has a great mentor, and an even better [persistent.dad]."
    Ev "Tiene un gran mentor, y un [persistent.dad] aún mejor."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:747
translate spanish d8a131_490848d8_2:

    # Ev "And I'm sure she knows that."
    Ev "Y estoy segura de que ella lo sabe."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:750
translate spanish d8a131_98d7819a:

    # Z "Thank you, [Ev]."
    Z "Gracias, [Ev]."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:754
translate spanish d8a131_b79ea889:

    # Z "It's not what I want for her."
    Z "No es lo que quiero para ella."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:755
translate spanish d8a131_9272b823:

    # Z "I know she is sometimes disappointed that I am so strict with her, but that's how it must be."
    Z "Sé que a veces le decepciona que sea tan estricto con ella, pero así debe ser."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:756
translate spanish d8a131_bdec78cd:

    # Z "And I will always support her, but she's going to find her own way, and that's a good thing."
    Z "Y siempre la apoyaré, pero va a encontrar su propio camino, y eso es algo bueno."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:759
translate spanish d8a131_d4bf4380_3:

    # Ev "Well then..."
    Ev "Pues entonces..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:762
translate spanish d8a131_94c040b6:

    # Ev "It's nice to have a supportive [persistent.dad]."
    Ev "Es agradable tener a un [persistent.dad] que te apoye."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:763
translate spanish d8a131_84c3b43a:

    # Ev "She's very lucky, and I'm sure she knows that."
    Ev "Ella es muy afortunada, y estoy segura de que lo sabe."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:766
translate spanish d8a131_98d7819a_1:

    # Z "Thank you, [Ev]."
    Z "Gracias, [Ev]."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:773
translate spanish d8a131_42d74e87:

    # Z "She will go her own way. My wife and I support her."
    Z "Seguirá su propio camino. Mi mujer y yo la apoyamos."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:776
translate spanish d8a131_d4bf4380_4:

    # Ev "Well then..."
    Ev "Pues entonces..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:779
translate spanish d8a131_94c040b6_1:

    # Ev "It's nice to have a supportive [persistent.dad]."
    Ev "Es agradable tener a un [persistent.dad] que te apoye."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:780
translate spanish d8a131_84c3b43a_1:

    # Ev "She's very lucky, and I'm sure she knows that."
    Ev "Ella es muy afortunada, y estoy segura de que lo sabe."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:783
translate spanish d8a131_98d7819a_2:

    # Z "Thank you, [Ev]."
    Z "Gracias, [Ev]."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:789
translate spanish d8a143x4_ed3f8649:

    # Zt "It's getting late. I should call it a night."
    Zt "Se hace tarde. Debería dar por terminada la noche."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:792
translate spanish d8a143x4_4fadaad5:

    # Z "[S], I'll be in the tent."
    Z "[S], estaré en la tienda."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:795
translate spanish d8a143x4_8b5cba01:

    # S "Alright, [persistent.dad]."
    S "Muy bien, [persistent.dad]."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:796
translate spanish d8a143x4_1a490955:

    # S "I'll join you soon."
    S "Me reuniré contigo enseguida."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:799
translate spanish d8a143x4_edeaae49:

    # "You say goodbye to the others and head back to the tent..."
    "Te despides de los demás y te diriges a la tienda..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:802
translate spanish d8a143x4_410237b9:

    # Zt "[S] seems much more relaxed now."
    Zt "[S] ahora parece mucho más relajada."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:805
translate spanish d8a143x4_4e9a65d6:

    # Zt "It's been an emotionally exhausting day; not only for her."
    Zt "Ha sido un día emocionalmente agotador; no sólo para ella."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:809
translate spanish d8a143x4_b9bf0c90:

    # "Once you have made yourself comfortable, you hear steps approaching, outside the tent."
    "Una vez que te has puesto cómodo, oyes unos pasos que se acercan, fuera de la tienda.."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:813
translate spanish d8a143x4_d602bcdd:

    # S "Knock, knock!"
    S "¡Toc, toc!"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:814
translate spanish d8a143x4_d8a79d89:

    # Z "You may come inside."
    Z "Puedes entrar."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:817
translate spanish d8a143x4_c663f0d6:

    # S "Really, may I? {i}*laughs*{/i}"
    S "De verdad, ¿puedo? {i}*risas*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:820
translate spanish d8a143x4_03feb90c:

    # S "It's warm in here."
    S "Aquí hace calor."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:821
translate spanish d8a143x4_595436a7:

    # Z "It is."
    Z "Así es."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:824
translate spanish d8a143x4_334a6b7b:

    # S "Let me put that there..."
    S "Déjame poner esto ahí..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:827
translate spanish d8a143x4_48c3a5bd:

    # S "I see you didn't wait even a minute to get undressed."
    S "Veo que no has esperado ni un minuto para desnudarte."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:828
translate spanish d8a143x4_bcf43de3:

    # Z "You know I don't like to sleep in a shirt."
    Z "Sabes que no me gusta dormir en camiseta."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:831
translate spanish d8a143x4_74bccdfc:

    # S "Eh, I know... like me with pants, right?"
    S "Eh, lo sé... como yo con pantalones, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:834
translate spanish d8a143x4_9ed00898:

    # Z "Ha! Well... enjoy the comfort, now you still have the option."
    Z "¡Ja!... Bueno... Disfruta de la comodidad, ahora que todavía tienes la opción."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:835
translate spanish d8a143x4_5c1f3e91:

    # S "You're saying I can't walk around in my underwear in the zone?"
    S "¿Dices que no puedo andar en ropa interior en la Zona?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:836
translate spanish d8a143x4_2796da5d:

    # Z "{i}*laughs*"
    Z "{i}*risas*"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:839
translate spanish d8a143x4_971a98df:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:842
translate spanish d8a143x4_971a98df_1:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:843
translate spanish d8a143x4_69035cd1:

    # Z "Is something wrong?"
    Z "¿Pasa algo malo?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:844
translate spanish d8a143x4_f1bca22a:

    # S "Hmm..."
    S "Hmm..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:847
translate spanish d8a143x4_5765c922:

    # S "I'm just thinking..."
    S "Sólo estoy pensando..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:850
translate spanish d8a143x4_3e34802e:

    # S "Right! I forgot the blanket!"
    S "Sí, claro. ¡Me olvidé de la manta!"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:853
translate spanish d8a143x4_56aade85:

    # "It takes [S] a minute, before she comes back..."
    "[S] tarda un minuto, antes de que ella vuelva..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:856
translate spanish d8a143x4_bbc8a0cb:

    # S "Got it."
    S "La tengo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:859
translate spanish d8a143x4_40f9b310:

    # Z "Good idea. We don't want to catch a cold when the fire goes out."
    Z "Buena idea. No queremos coger un resfriado cuando se apague el fuego."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:860
translate spanish d8a143x4_637e8f07:

    # S "Yup."
    S "Síp."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:863
translate spanish d8a143x4_dc324eff:

    # S "It's kind of like back when I was little, remember?"
    S "Es como cuando era pequeña, ¿lo recuerdas?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:866
translate spanish d8a143x4_b3df0d06:

    # Z "I do."
    Z "Lo hago."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:870
translate spanish d8a143x4_1cda6440:

    # Z "And once in bed, I would always say..."
    Z "Y una vez en la cama, siempre te decía..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:873
translate spanish d8a143x4_e30e8c29:

    # Z "It's a big day tomorrow. Time to sleep."
    Z "Mañana será un gran día. Es hora de dormir."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:877
translate spanish d8a143x4_a82f5885:

    # Z "And I used to stroke your cheek and tell you..."
    Z "Y yo solía acariciar tu mejilla y decirte..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:878
translate spanish d8a143x4_e30e8c29_1:

    # Z "It's a big day tomorrow. Time to sleep."
    Z "Mañana será un gran día. Es hora de dormir."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:881
translate spanish d8a143x4_7b3b9eb5:

