    S "No, es otra cosa..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:956
translate spanish d8a143x4_db714313_1:

    # S "Earlier, outside, while you were talking with [Ev], I had a short talk with [He]."
    S "Antes, fuera, mientras tú hablabas con [Ev], yo tuve una breve charla con [He]."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:960
translate spanish d8a174_46169a1c:

    # S "...and as we were talking about the Zone and everything, he said that it's best to not leave behind unfinished business before I go..."
    S "... y mientras hablábamos de la Zona y todo eso, dijo que es mejor no dejar asuntos pendientes antes de que me vaya..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:961
translate spanish d8a174_2c94df90:

    # S "...because you never know if you come back after all."
    S "... porque nunca se sabe si volverás después de todo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:964
translate spanish d8a174_ae53f13a:

    # Z "What do you mean? You will come back, I am sure. What did he tell you?"
    Z "¿Qué quieres decir? Estoy seguro de que volverás. ¿Qué te ha dicho?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:967
