    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:970
translate spanish d8a174_9e7c4048:

    # S "[persistent.dad!c], this whole day I was not worried about the Zone, or that I might not come back."
    S "[persistent.dad!c], durante todo este día no me preocupó la Zona, ni que pudiera no volver."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:971
translate spanish d8a174_8e932c55:

    # S "You taught me that I should face my challenges with a clear mind, so that I am not distracted."
    S "Me has enseñado que debo afrontar mis retos con la mente clara, para no distraerme."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:974
translate spanish d8a174_a9dd4364:

    # S "But if there are still things you want to do or say before you head into a place you don't know you will ever come back from..."
