# game/scripts/day8.rpy:977
translate spanish d8a174_ab62c9b2:

    # Z "...then you will be distracted; it's inevitable, really."
    Z "... entonces te distraerás; es inevitable, de verdad."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:978
translate spanish d8a174_971a98df_1:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:981
translate spanish d8a174_4599f48b:

    # S "I don't know if you remember the other day, when we were on the balcony..."
    S "No sé si recuerdas el otro día, cuando estábamos en el balcón..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:982
translate spanish d8a174_9bd67412:

    # S "We were talking about what I know and don't know, what plans I have..."
    S "Estábamos hablando de lo que sé y no sé, de los planes que tengo..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:985
translate spanish d8a174_1a3a8933:

    # S "...I was telling you that there are a few things that are clear to me, even if I wasn't leaving just yet."
    S "... Te decía que hay algunas cosas que tengo claras, aunque no me vaya todavía."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:988
translate spanish d8a174_109a50f2:

    # S "...that I know what I don't want to lose."
    S "... que sé lo que no quiero perder."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:992
translate spanish d8a174_38ba5527:

    # S "...and that is our family."
    S "... y esa es nuestra familia."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:995
translate spanish d8a174_bcd5c49e:

    # S "I agree that I should forge my own path as a Stalker, but I don't want this to mean that I am leaving all of you behind."
    S "Estoy de acuerdo en que debo forjar mi propio camino como Acechadora, pero no quiero que esto signifique que os deje atrás a todos vosotros."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:996
translate spanish d8a174_4c2360a9:

    # S "The same way you have taught me about being a Stalker, [persistent.mom] has always taught us that family is important and that we should value it."
    S "Del mismo modo que tú me has enseñado a ser una Acechadora, [persistent.mom] siempre nos ha enseñado que la familia es importante y que debemos valorarla."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:999
translate spanish d8a174_7a82caf0:

    # S "I love being a part of that. When I return from the Zone, will you let me stay?"
    S "Me encanta ser parte de esto. Cuando vuelva de la Zona, ¿me dejarás quedarme?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1002
translate spanish d8a174_1381ff68:

    # Z "[S]... I will never send you away from me, from us. Stalker or not Stalker, you are family. [W] is right."
    Z "[S]... Nunca te alejaré de mí, de nosotros. Acechadora o no Acechadora, eres de la familia. [W] tiene razón."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1003
translate spanish d8a174_ef24a9d3:

    # Z "Have I ever made you feel unwelcome or told you that once you became a Stalker you were on your own?"
    Z "¿Alguna vez te he hecho sentir que no eres bienvenida o te he dicho que una vez que te convirtieras en una Acechadora estarías sola?"

