    # Z "I should have been more clear about that then. Our family is and will always have a place for you, wherever your path may lead after this."
    Z "Tendría que haber sido más claro entonces. Nuestra familia tiene y tendrá siempre un lugar para ti, sea cual sea tu camino después de esto."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1012
translate spanish d8a174_d5439bb5:

    # S "Thank you, [persistent.dad]. That takes a weight off my shoulders."
    S "Gracias, [persistent.dad]. Eso me quita un peso de encima."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1015
translate spanish d8a174_5d1cf7b7:

    # "Reassured, [S] settles into your embrace, finding comfort in it, as you share a tender moment."
    "Tranquilizada, [S] se acomoda en tu abrazo, encontrando consuelo en él, mientras compartís un tierno momento."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1018
translate spanish d8a174_4da8aa7b:

    # Z "I am glad we cleared that up. Let's sleep now."
    Z "Me alegro de que hayamos aclarado esto. Ahora vamos a dormir."

