translate spanish d8b_b2a0719f:

    # "You remember how to access the entrance to the cave and head inside..."
    "Recuerdas cómo acceder a la entrada de la cueva y dirigirte al interior..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1754
translate spanish d8b_65f994c3:

    # Zt "Great..."
    Zt "Genial..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1755
translate spanish d8b_203ae126:

    # Zt "I have no idea what the code to open the gate is."
    Zt "No tengo ni idea de cuál es el código para abrir la puerta."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1756
translate spanish d8b_b69a8c75:

    # Z "Hello? Anyone here?"
    Z "¿Hola? ¿Hay alguien aquí?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1757
translate spanish d8b_733f21a5:

    # "Nothing happens."
    "No pasa nada."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1760
translate spanish d8b_17808bec:

    # Z "{i}*sighs*"
    Z "{i}*suspiros*"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1763
translate spanish d8b_b695b6a9:

    # Zt "That must be one of those elevating platforms..."
    Zt "Esta debe ser una de esas plataformas elevadoras..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1766
translate spanish d8b_7aeb094f:

    # Zt "Maybe I can get their attention some other way."
    Zt "Tal vez pueda llamar su atención de otra manera."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1769
translate spanish d8b_74453c9a:

    # Zt "I wonder where this door leads to."
    Zt "Me pregunto a dónde conducirá esta puerta."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1772
translate spanish d8b_cfbe5196:

    # Zt "Let's see what happens if I pull this lever..."
    Zt "A ver qué pasa si tiro de esta palanca..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1775
translate spanish d8b_06d41db9:

    # "The door behind you opens..."
    "La puerta detrás de ti se abre..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1776
translate spanish d8b_6689bf39:

    # C "Enemy or friend. Curious."
    C "Enemigo o amigo. Curioso."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1778
translate spanish d8b_581947dc:

    # C "Speak or die. Certain."
    C "Habla o muere. Ciertamente."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1779
translate spanish d8b_03dd6837:

    # "The voice came from right behind you. Although you identify the person behind you as female, it sounded like two or more voices spoke at the same time."
    "La voz viene de justo detrás de ti. Aunque identificas a la persona que está detrás de ti como una mujer, parece que hablaron dos o más voces al mismo tiempo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1780
translate spanish d8b_6005a4cc:

    # "Its surprisingly commanding and alienating tone making you uncomfortable..."
    "Su tono sorprendentemente dominante y enajenante te incomoda..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1786
translate spanish d8b_d3c264bc:

    # Mu "..."
    Mu "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1790
translate spanish d8b_ed0b5c13:

    # Z "My name is [persistent.player_name], I'm here to speak with Fangs."
    Z "Me llamo [persistent.player_name], estoy aquí para hablar con Fangs."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1791
translate spanish d8b_1de86dd4:

    # Z "She wanted to see me again."
    Z "Ella quería volver a verme."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1792
translate spanish d8b_d3c264bc_1:

    # Mu "..."
    Mu "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1795
translate spanish d8b_29c5cb56:

    # "She looks startled..."
    "Parece asustada..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1796
translate spanish d8b_51c3205f:

    # Mu "We know you. Two-sided. Precarious."
    Mu "Te reconocemos. Dos caras. Precario."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1799
translate spanish d8b_ee78040e:

    # Mu "Follow us. Close by."
    Mu "Síguenos. De cerca."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1800
translate spanish d8b_7412dee9:

    # Mu "We bring you inside, then keep guard."
    Mu "Te llevaremos dentro y luego haremos guardia."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1805
translate spanish d8b_f8dd53a7:

    # Z "I didn't expect someone that cute when I heard that voice."
    Z "No esperaba a alguien tan mona cuando escuché esa voz."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1808
translate spanish d8b_73349b3c:

    # Mu "Cute, we are..."
    Mu "Mona, lo somos..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1809
translate spanish d8b_13c6a427:

    # Mu "Mate with us you want. Evident."
    Mu "Si quieres, puedes aparearte con nosotras. Evidente."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1812
translate spanish d8b_a2d19126:

    # Mu "Not one of them. Conscious."
    Mu "No es uno de ellos. Consciente."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1813
translate spanish d8b_1e7e820a:

    # Mu "No interest we have."
    Mu "No tenemos ningún interés."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1816
translate spanish d8b_a8b53145:

    # Mu "We know you. Orders given. Need to come with us."
    Mu "Te conocemos. Órdenes dadas. Necesitas venir con nosotras."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1817
translate spanish d8b_7412dee9_1:

    # Mu "We bring you inside, then keep guard."
    Mu "Te llevaremos dentro y luego haremos guardia."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1822
translate spanish d8b_47904225:

    # Z "Can you be less unsettling?"
    Z "¿Puedes ser menos inquietante?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1826
translate spanish d8b_9f83625b:

    # Mu "We... unsettling..."
    Mu "Nosotras... inquietantes..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1831
translate spanish d8b_5e236c51:

    # Mu "We are different."
    Mu "Somos diferentes."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1832
translate spanish d8b_4b8a092e:

    # Mu "Not unsettling here, they promised."
    Mu "Aquí no hay nada inquietante, lo prometieron."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1833
translate spanish d8b_bcba4f1e:

    # Mu "Guarding this place. Safe. Accepted."
    Mu "Guardando este lugar. Seguro. Aceptado."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1836
translate spanish d8b_581c067c:

    # Mu "We take eyes for revenge. Do not want to."
    Mu "Llevamos los ojos para la venganza. No queremos hacerlo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1839
translate spanish d8b_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1842
translate spanish d8b_ae53ee53:

    # Mu "But we know you. Order to let you pass."
    Mu "Pero te conocemos. Orden de dejarte pasar."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1843
translate spanish d8b_329397da:

    # Mu "You follow us. No more words."
    Mu "Síguenos. No más palabras."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1844
translate spanish d8b_7412dee9_2:

    # Mu "We bring you inside, then keep guard."
    Mu "Te llevaremos dentro y luego haremos guardia."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1851
translate spanish d8b17_504a6a94:

    # "She uses the keypad to open up the gate once more and tells you to look out for the command center, then, without saying a word, goes back into her room."
    "Utiliza el teclado para abrir la puerta una vez más y te dice que estés atento al centro de mando, luego, sin decir una palabra, vuelve a su sala."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1852
translate spanish d8b17_f70f5f34:

    # "The base is structured like some of the old military bases you have explored in the past, and after some minutes you find your way to the room where Fangs is supposed to be."
    "La base está estructurada como algunas de las antiguas bases militares que has explorado en el pasado, y tras unos minutos encuentras el camino hacia la sala donde se supone que está Fangs."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1856
translate spanish d8b17_3774cdae:

    # Zt "This must be it."
    Zt "Esto debe ser."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1859
translate spanish d8b17_fa52cf7a:

    # Muw "Three, six, nine..."
    Muw "Tres, seis, nueve..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1862
translate spanish d8b17_868bfd9b:

    # Fa "So this is everything we have..."
    Fa "Así que esto es todo lo que tenemos..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1863
translate spanish d8b17_79eb2e7f:

    # Fa "She said her people change over time, did she at least go into detail?"
    Fa "Ella dijo que su pueblo cambia con el tiempo, ¿al menos entró en detalles?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1866
translate spanish d8b17_86475774:

    # Pe "She did not, but I still think it's a good opportunity."
    Pe "No lo hizo, pero sigo pensando que es una buena oportunidad."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1867
translate spanish d8b17_93ed76e1:

    # Pe "The place is not that far away from here, chances are high that-"
    Pe "El lugar no está tan lejos de aquí, hay muchas posibilidades de que..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1868
translate spanish d8b17_1712cde0:

    # "You cough..."
    "Toses..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1871
translate spanish d8b17_99ce154e:

    # Fa "Yeah, what is it..."
    Fa "Sí, ¿qué es?..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1872
translate spanish d8b17_2e3987c0:

    # Pe "..."
    Pe "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1875
translate spanish d8b17_5f329513:

    # Fa "Ah, [persistent.player_name], I knew it, welcome back."
    Fa "Ah, [persistent.player_name], lo sabía, bienvenido."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1878
translate spanish d8b17_47a0be2d:

    # Fa "None of the people in this place reduce Pepper to silence like you do. I am not sure she likes you."
    Fa "Ninguna de las personas de este lugar reduce a Pepper al silencio como tú. No estoy segura de que le gustes."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1881
translate spanish d8b17_1a182952:

    # Fa "I was almost ready to reach out to you again."
    Fa "Estaba casi lista para contactar contigo de nuevo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1882
translate spanish d8b17_ce13abb1:

    # Fa "But here you are, deciding to take the initiative..."
    Fa "Pero aquí estás, decidiendo tomar la iniciativa..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1885
translate spanish d8b17_de1bef04:

    # Fa "Pepper, leave us alone will you."
    Fa "Pepper, déjanos solos, ¿quieres?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1886
translate spanish d8b17_54612163:

    # Fa "And thank you for your report. I will have to think about it."
    Fa "Y gracias por tu informe. Tendré que pensar en ello."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1889
translate spanish d8b17_2e3987c0_1:

    # Pe "..."
    Pe "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1892
translate spanish d8b17_179d67a5:

    # Pe "{i}*sighs*"
    Pe "{i}*suspiros*"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1895
translate spanish d8b17_eddaa2ce:

    # "Everyone except you and Fangs leaves the room..."
    "Todos excepto tú y Fangs salen de la habitación..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1898
translate spanish d8b17_2348f031:

    # Fa "So... are you here to help us?"
    Fa "Entonces... ¿estás aquí para ayudarnos?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1899
translate spanish d8b17_cb228f0c:

    # Z "I am not making any promises until I know your end goals."
    Z "No te voy a hacer ninguna promesa hasta que conozca tus objetivos finales."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1902
translate spanish d8b17_02808cac:

    # Fa "I already told you, we do this to get our rightful spot in Zeta."
    Fa "Ya te lo he dicho, lo hacemos para conseguir el lugar que nos corresponde en Zeta."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1905
translate spanish d8b17_f1287dcd:

    # Z "You want me to help you destroy my home city and start a war that kills everyone?"
    Z "¿Quieres que te ayude a destruir mi ciudad natal y a iniciar una guerra que mate a todo el mundo?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1906
translate spanish d8b17_6a7c6563:

    # Z "You think this is why I came back?"
    Z "¿Crees que por eso he vuelto?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1909
translate spanish d8b17_ff8d00a0:

    # Fa "I don't know why you would help us, and it's not my job to care for it."
    Fa "No sé por qué nos ayudarías, y no es mi trabajo interesarme por ello."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1912
translate spanish d8b17_352e4d2d:

    # Fa "The only way to get to a normal life for those who are like us is to claim what we have been denied to get for centuries."
    Fa "La única manera de llegar a una vida normal para los que somos como nosotros es reclamar lo que nos han negado obtener durante siglos."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1913
translate spanish d8b17_8533d5c0:

    # Z "If I didn't talk to you before I'd say you're either stupid or mental."
    Z "Si no hubiera hablado contigo antes, diría que eres estúpida o que estás loca."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1916
translate spanish d8b17_d65efcac:

    # Fa "...What?"
    Fa "... ¿Qué?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1917
translate spanish d8b17_388d67fb:

    # Z "But since I know better, I say you're planning a pathetic jihad that will only lead to everyone's death."
    Z "Pero como te conozco mejor, digo que estás tramando una patética cruzada que sólo conducirá a la muerte de todos."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1918
translate spanish d8b17_7d2fbc90:

    # Z "Ironic, since you seem to be so protective of your people in here."
    Z "Irónico, ya que pareces ser bastante protectora con tu gente en este lugar."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1919
translate spanish d8b17_6535d2dc:

    # Z "But you must know that you're denying reality if you think that a few hundred mutants in pre-war armor can win against thousands of Zetans, once it becomes an open war."
    Z "Pero debes saber que estás negando la realidad si piensas que unos pocos cientos de mutantes con armaduras de la era prebélica pueden ganar contra miles de Zetanos, una vez que se convierta en una guerra abierta."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1922
translate spanish d8b17_af2c96cf:

    # Fa "How... dare you call this a suicide mission."
    Fa "Cómo... te atreves a llamar a esto una misión suicida."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1925
translate spanish d8b17_f06f3655:

    # Fa "I have built up this place and planned this mission for months."
    Fa "He construido este lugar y planeado esta misión durante meses."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1926
translate spanish d8b17_a56671d0:

    # Fa "Most of the people in here have suffered through things Zetans wouldn't even imagine!"
    Fa "La mayoría de los que están aquí han sufrido cosas que los Zetanos ni siquiera imaginan."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1927
translate spanish d8b17_d2fa2feb:

    # Fa "That city of discriminating snobs doesn't know how the world out there is, and you know it."
    Fa "Esa ciudad de pijos discriminadores no sabe cómo es el mundo de ahí fuera, y tú lo sabes."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1930
translate spanish d8b17_79d3b4fa:

    # Fa "They will never know what it's like to be us until they get what they deserve!"
    Fa "¡Nunca sabrán lo que es ser nosotros hasta que reciban su merecido!"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1931
translate spanish d8b17_bc4fb98b:

    # Z "You are going to get your people killed if you start an open conflict."
    Z "Vas a conseguir que maten a tu gente si inicias un conflicto abierto."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1934
translate spanish d8b17_70f6c4a2:

    # Z "And even if you win, you will never get the population on your side, no matter how much technology and firepower you pile onto your soldiers."
    Z "Y aunque ganes, nunca lograrás que la población esté de tu lado, no importa cuánta tecnología y potencia de fuego le pongas a tus soldados."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1935
translate spanish d8b17_29583b68:

    # Z "The city has existed for over 400 years, Fangs, and it's been ever growing."
    Z "La ciudad existe desde hace más de 400 años, Fangs, y no deja de crecer."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1936
translate spanish d8b17_7b8f9141:

    # Z "So get your head straight. A nation that has been in control of their territory for so long will never surrender it."
    Z "Así que ponte las pilas. Una nación que ha tenido el control de su territorio durante tanto tiempo nunca lo cederá."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1937
translate spanish d8b17_cb8cbf59:

    # Fa "..."
    Fa "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1940
translate spanish d8b17_76360a30:

    # "She gets up..."
    "Se levanta..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1943
translate spanish d8b17_cb8cbf59_1:

    # Fa "..."
    Fa "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1944
translate spanish d8b17_e75ef736:

    # Fa "Everyone in here is out for retaliation, [persistent.player_name]."
    Fa "Todo el mundo aquí tiene ganas de vengarse, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1945
translate spanish d8b17_8d8a5254:

    # Fa "And I am giving them what they want."
    Fa "Y les estoy dando lo que quieren."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1948
translate spanish d8b17_910b2373:

    # Fa "{i}*sighs*"
    Fa "{i}*suspiros*"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1949
translate spanish d8b17_cb8cbf59_2:

    # Fa "..."
    Fa "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1950
translate spanish d8b17_9b09a474:

    # Fa "...I know that you are right."
    Fa "... Sé que tienes razón."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1951
translate spanish d8b17_27ebc2b4:

    # Fa "We have been in this bunker for so long, telling each other that everything is possible."
    Fa "Llevamos mucho tiempo en este búnker, diciéndonos que todo es posible."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1952
translate spanish d8b17_f1d8944a:

    # Fa "That is what we want to believe... but..."
    Fa "Eso es lo que queremos creer... pero..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1953
translate spanish d8b17_91e69c39:

    # Fa "Maybe that is also why Ivy brought you in after all."
    Fa "Tal vez también sea por eso por lo que Ivy te trajo, después de todo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1956
translate spanish d8b17_c40f96b3:

    # Fa "So... what do you propose?"
    Fa "Entonces... ¿qué propones?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1961
translate spanish d8b17_cdf44b40:

    # Z "I will help your people as long as you swear not to start an open conflict."
    Z "Ayudaré a tu pueblo mientras jures no iniciar un conflicto abierto."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1962
translate spanish d8b17_05638a48:

    # Z "Come here and I will explain it to you."
    Z "Ven aquí y te lo contaré."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1965
translate spanish d8b17_30ce271e:

    # "She walks over, standing before you..."
    "Ella se acerca y se pone delante de ti..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1968
translate spanish d8b17_cb8cbf59_3:

    # Fa "..."
    Fa "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1969
translate spanish d8b17_b15a57e9:

    # Z "Now listen..."
    Z "Ahora escucha..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1970
translate spanish d8b17_a8169cb3:

    # Z "Your army is small, and your equipment is limited."
    Z "Tu ejército es pequeño y tu equipo es limitado."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1971
translate spanish d8b17_80ccbac0:

    # Z "Fighting your way through everything is not an option."
    Z "Luchar contra todo no es una opción."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1972
translate spanish d8b17_9d741ff7:

    # Z "So what you need is allies. Allies from the outside, and allies in the city."
    Z "Así que lo que necesitas son aliados. Aliados de fuera, y aliados en la ciudad."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1973
translate spanish d8b17_6c799807:

    # Z "Scrap the idea of going to war. What you need is influence."
    Z "Desecha la idea de ir a la guerra. Lo que necesitas es influencia."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1976
translate spanish d8b17_8272f811:

    # Z "Your hatred for the Queen is useless, I have met her."
    Z "Tu odio hacia la Reina es inútil, la conozco."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1979
translate spanish d8b17_c109672f:

    # Fa "So you can influence her..."
    Fa "Para que puedas influir en ella..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1982
translate spanish d8b17_b8a8e04b:

    # Z "Maybe I will."
    Z "Tal vez lo haga."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1983
translate spanish d8b17_744ce8db:

    # Z "Zeta has, on the whole, bigger problems than to focus on enforcing the tradition of excluding and subjugating mutants."
    Z "Zeta tiene, en general, problemas más grandes que centrarse en hacer cumplir la tradición de excluir y subyugar a los mutantes."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1984
translate spanish d8b17_b19c6039:

    # Z "If you scrap your plan of becoming a hostile force and instead let me work on this diplomatically, the city could become more tolerant to your people."
    Z "Si descartas tu plan de convertirte en una fuerza hostil y en cambio me dejas trabajar en esto diplomáticamente, la ciudad podría volverse más tolerante con tu gente."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1985
translate spanish d8b17_9648cba2:

    # Z "Especially if you can present yourself as a viable ally."
    Z "Especialmente si puedes presentarte como un aliado viable."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1988
translate spanish d8b17_98ecafb1:

    # Fa "We don't have the numbers to be a credible ally yet."
    Fa "Todavía no tenemos los números para ser unos aliados creíbles."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1991
translate spanish d8b17_c61a0752:

    # Z "That is also correct."
    Z "Eso también es cierto."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1994
translate spanish d8b17_d5d5d3f0:

    # Fa "Luckily I am already preparing to solve that issue."
    Fa "Por suerte, ya me estoy preparando para resolver esa cuestión."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:1996
translate spanish d8b17_da034ae3:

    # Fa "I need to verify some things first though, so why don't you take the time to get settled?"
    Fa "Pero antes necesito verificar algunas cosas, así que ¿por qué no te tomas el tiempo necesario para instalarte?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2004
translate spanish re_d8b17_6e037dd7:

    # Z "...?"
    Z "¿...?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2007
translate spanish re_d8b17_aeeda36a:

    # Faw "I have to admit..."
    Faw "Tengo que admitir que..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2008
translate spanish re_d8b17_27050734:

    # Faw "I knew you had it in you after our fight last time."
    Faw "... sabía que lo tenías después de nuestra última pelea."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2009
translate spanish re_d8b17_edf3bbd9:

    # Faw "But you're showing that you have brains, not just brawn."
    Faw "Pero estás demostrando que tienes cerebro, no sólo fuerza muscular."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2010
translate spanish re_d8b17_a895e7d3:

    # Faw "You might just be the man we need around here..."
    Faw "Puede que seas el hombre que necesitamos aquí..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2013
translate spanish re_d8b17_049e8c5a:

