    Fa "Entonces... debemos prepararnos."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2319
translate spanish re_d8b17_173f45a7:

    # Fa "It was nice getting to know you, [persistent.player_name]. Even if it was short lived."
    Fa "Ha sido un placer conocerte, [persistent.player_name]. Aunque haya durado poco."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2323
translate spanish re_d8b17_b2f02613:

    # "Fangs eventually escorts you out. You're sure that you won't hear see any of the mutants anytime soon, but you decided that it's best that they fight their own battles."
    "Al final, Fangs te acompaña a la salida. Está seguro de que no va a ver a ninguno de los mutantes en breve, pero ha decidido que es mejor que luchen sus propias batallas."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2329
translate spanish re_d8b17_7b374447_3:

    # "You make out for a while..."
    "Os enrolláis un rato..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2332
translate spanish re_d8b17_b257c3ea_3:

    # Fa "That was nice..."
    Fa "Esto ha estado bien..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2333
translate spanish re_d8b17_e8f32ca2:

    # Fa "I have to go back to work now."
    Fa "Tengo que volver al trabajo ahora."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2334
translate spanish re_d8b17_173f45a7_1:

    # Fa "It was nice getting to know you, [persistent.player_name]. Even if it was short lived."
    Fa "Ha sido un placer conocerte, [persistent.player_name]. Aunque haya durado poco."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2338
translate spanish re_d8b17_b2f02613_1:

    # "Fangs eventually escorts you out. You're sure that you won't hear see any of the mutants anytime soon, but you decided that it's best that they fight their own battles."
    "Al final, Fangs te acompaña a la salida. Está seguro de que no va a ver a ninguno de los mutantes en breve, pero ha decidido que es mejor que luchen sus propias batallas."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2345
translate spanish d8b65_dfe533d2:

    # "As you both get up, Fangs returns to her desk, focusing again on the work she did before you entered the room."
    "Mientras ambos os levantáis, Fangs vuelve a su escritorio, concentrándose de nuevo en el trabajo que hacía antes de que entrarais en la sala."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2346
translate spanish d8b65_ea9c6e81:

    # "As other soldiers come and go, you take a look at the locker you have been assigned..."
    "Mientras otros soldados van y vienen, echas un vistazo a la taquilla que te han asignado..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2349
translate spanish d8b65_3bb5d54e:

    # Zt "So, this is a thing now..."
    Zt "Así que, ahora esto es una cosa..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2350
translate spanish d8b65_5f2bca30:

    # Zt "A few weeks ago I could have never imagined a place like this still existed, or that I would find myself trying to help out a bunch of mutants. Yet, here I am."
    Zt "Hace unas semanas nunca hubiera imaginado que un lugar como este todavía existía, o que me encontraría tratando de ayudar a un grupo de mutantes. Sin embargo, aquí estoy.."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2353
translate spanish d8b65_68c4f65c:

    # Zt "I don't know where this is going, but the equipment this place holds could be a chance to change everything for these people."
    Zt "No sé a dónde va esto, pero el equipo que tiene este lugar podría ser una oportunidad para cambiar todo para estas personas."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2354
translate spanish d8b65_03791207:

    # Zt "That is, as long as they play their cards right."
    Zt "Es decir, siempre que jueguen bien sus cartas."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2356
translate spanish d8b65_57c8eefb:

    # Zt "...?"
    Zt "¿...?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2359
translate spanish d8b65_65f920ad:

    # Fa "Ivy, you're back, finally."
    Fa "Ivy, has vuelto, por fin."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2362
translate spanish d8b65_6907d08e:

    # Fa "Ready for a new mission? Pepper managed to get some new information out of the weird one."
    Fa "¿Lista para una nueva misión? Pepper se las arregló para sacarle una nueva información a la rara."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2363
translate spanish d8b65_fc4de666:

    # Fa "Oh, and [persistent.player_name] came back and decided to help us out."
    Fa "Oh, y [persistent.player_name] volvió y decidió ayudarnos."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2366
translate spanish d8b65_908cf232:

    # Fa "It looks like your intuition is paying off, once again."
    Fa "Parece que tu intuición da sus frutos, una vez más."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2367
translate spanish d8b65_367ba300:

    # Fa "Ha... I can see those eyes turn green from here."
    Fa "Ja... Puedo ver cómo esos ojos se vuelven verdes desde aquí."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2368
translate spanish d8b65_5018f220:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2371
translate spanish d8b65_5018f220_1:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2377
translate spanish d8b65_7981d09c:

    # Zt "She's an archer?"
    Zt "¿Ella es una arquera?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2378
translate spanish d8b65_60dab136:

    # Fa "Hey, [persistent.player_name]."
    Fa "Ey, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2379
translate spanish d8b65_8424e6db:

    # Fa "I think I am done here, let me know when you're ready to plan your first mission with us."
    Fa "Creo que he terminado aquí, avísame cuando estés listo para planificar tu primera misión con nosotros."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2380
translate spanish d8b65_2fcbbb37:

    # Z "I will."
    Z "Lo haré."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2386
translate spanish d8b76_eb755fce:

    # Z "So... what about that place to the east of here?"
    Z "Entonces... ¿Qué pasa con ese lugar al este de aquí?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2387
translate spanish d8b76_c19b85a8:

    # Z "It says something about a hive?"
    Z "¿Dice algo sobre una colmena?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2390
translate spanish d8b76_6432b102:

    # Fa "Yeah, that...I am still a bit iffy on the specifics, but it has potential."
    Fa "Sí, eso... Todavía estoy un poco indecisa sobre los detalles, pero tiene potencial."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2391
translate spanish d8b76_f36d18f5:

    # Fa "If you want to help us with this one, there's someone you should listen to."
    Fa "Si quieres ayudarnos con esto, hay alguien a quien deberías escuchar."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2395
translate spanish d8b76_ab58713d:

    # Fa "Soldier, have the new girl report to me."
    Fa "Soldado, que la chica nueva me informe."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2396
translate spanish d8b76_ef9cf921:

    # Mu "Yes, Commander."
    Mu "Sí, Comandante."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2397
translate spanish d8b76_a20cefa7:

    # "..."
    "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2398
translate spanish d8b76_f174f685:

    # Fa "Do you know her?"
    Fa "¿La conoces?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2400
translate spanish d8b76_c280e36c:

    # Z "Not really... but when I got here, she was guarding the entrance."
    Z "En realidad no... pero cuando llegué aquí, ella estaba vigilando la entrada."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2401
translate spanish d8b76_7287631c:

    # Fa "Ah... yes. I'd forgotten about that."
    Fa "Ah... sí. Lo había olvidado."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2404
translate spanish d8b76_7661535e:

    # Fa "Listen up girl, our friend here is going to help us, but he needs to know more about the situation."
    Fa "Escucha chica, nuestro amigo va a ayudarnos, pero necesita saber más sobre la situación."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2407
translate spanish d8b76_04177937:

    # Fa "So talk to him."
    Fa "Así que habla con él."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2410
translate spanish d8b76_d3c264bc:

    # Mu "..."
    Mu "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2411
translate spanish d8b76_f565348a:

    # Fa "Come on, speak. What were you looking for, when my soldiers found you?"
    Fa "Vamos, habla. ¿Qué estabas buscando cuando mis soldados te encontraron?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2414
translate spanish d8b76_2f9caeb4:

    # Mu "We came here to avoid the darkness."
    Mu "Vinimos aquí para evitar la oscuridad."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2415
translate spanish d8b76_bf9bb791:

    # "Like in your previous encounter, her voice is unsettling, layered as if composed by multiple voices."
    "Como en tu anterior encuentro, su voz es inquietante, en capas, como si estuviera compuesta por múltiples voces."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2416
translate spanish d8b76_5b4bd952:

    # Mu "Impatient. Mother is waiting for us."
    Mu "Impaciente. Madre nos está esperando."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2417
translate spanish d8b76_210532d3:

    # Mu "We are not ready to see it yet. Too curious."
    Mu "Todavía no estamos preparados para verlo. Demasiada curiosidad."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2420
translate spanish d8b76_43c156e3:

    # Fa "See, [persistent.player_name]. She's frustratingly hard to make sense of."
    Fa "Lo ves, [persistent.player_name]. Ella es frustrantemente difícil de entender."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2421
translate spanish d8b76_8c0d3fe9:

    # Fa "Pepper and I have been looking into this for a few days now."
    Fa "Pepper y yo llevamos unos días investigando."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2422
translate spanish d8b76_18759e90:

    # Fa "Basically, some of my scouts found a place not too far from here, that has been isolated for a long time. That's where she's from."
    Fa "Básicamente, algunos de mis exploradores encontraron un lugar no muy lejos de aquí, que ha estado aislado durante mucho tiempo. De ahí viene ella."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2423
translate spanish d8b76_ca7fefb6:

    # Fa "They found her roaming the dunes. She seemed lost."
    Fa "La encontraron vagando por las dunas. Parecía perdida."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2424
translate spanish d8b76_3fb571ab:

    # Fa "From what she tells us, her people are also mutants like her, all of them. They could strengthen our numbers considerably."
    Fa "Por lo que nos cuenta, su gente también son mutantes como ella, todos ellos. Podrían reforzar nuestro número considerablemente."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2425
translate spanish d8b76_dd04d5c7:

    # Fa "Soldier, we need you to lead us to where you come from, and introduce us to your people, so we will take you with us."
    Fa "Soldado, necesitamos que nos guíes hasta tu lugar de origen y nos presentes a tu gente, para que te llevemos con nosotros."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2428
translate spanish d8b76_69f3d998:

    # Mu "But... we are not sure to go there yet."
    Mu "Pero... no estamos seguros de ir allí todavía."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2429
translate spanish d8b76_a5ab1158:

    # Mu "Mother will be waiting for us, wanting us to join."
    Mu "Madre nos estará esperando, queriendo que nos unamos."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2430
translate spanish d8b76_8be2edef:

    # Z "What do you mean by that?"
    Z "¿Qué quieres decir con eso?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2431
translate spanish d8b76_c9f7c460:

    # Mu "Mother needs us. In darkness. To serve the Hive that serves us."
    Mu "Madre nos necesita. En la oscuridad. Para servir a la Colmena que nos sirve."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2432
translate spanish d8b76_47e2134a:

    # Mu "Leaving, impossible."
    Mu "Salir, imposible."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2435
translate spanish d8b76_cdc743f4:

    # Fa "We need you there as a show of good faith from our part."
    Fa "Te necesitamos allí como muestra de buena fe por nuestra parte."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2438
translate spanish d8b76_1a67ceb9:

    # Mu "We understand. Mediation. Conflict a possibility."
    Mu "Lo entendemos. La mediación. El conflicto es una posibilidad."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2441
translate spanish d8b76_e250c4d9:

    # Fa "Something like that, yes... I think."
    Fa "Algo así, sí... creo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2442
translate spanish d8b76_87f4386f:

    # Fa "Anyway, you are one of us now, and if that is your choice, we will not leave you there, but we do need your help."
    Fa "De todos modos, ahora eres una de nosotros, y si esa es tu elección, no te dejaremos ahí, pero necesitamos tu ayuda."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2445
translate spanish d8b76_1d4d4c64:

    # Mu "Good promise. Ignorance, maybe. Doubt."
    Mu "Buena promesa. Ignorancia, es posible Duda."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2448
translate spanish d8b76_2b082697:

    # Z "We will do our best to talk to your people and persuade them to join this group. Would you help us with this?"
    Z "Haremos todo lo posible para hablar con tu gente y convencerla de que se una a este grupo. ¿Nos ayudarías con eso?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2449
translate spanish d8b76_bdac41ba:

    # Mu "We can try."
    Mu "Podemos intentarlo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2450
translate spanish d8b76_20beaf36:

    # Fa "You can take a seat."
    Fa "Puedes sentarte."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2451
translate spanish d8b76_d496f304:

    # Z "We do have more questions about this Hive you talk of."
    Z "Tenemos más preguntas sobre esa Colmena de la que hablas."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2454
translate spanish d8b76_0c0ae700:

    # "It takes some time for you to find a way to resonate with this mutant, but her answers remain cryptic and vague, especially about her people."
    "Te lleva algún tiempo encontrar una forma de conectar con esta mutante, pero sus respuestas siguen siendo crípticas e imprecisas, especialmente sobre su pueblo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2455
translate spanish d8b76_19ad312e:

    # Fa "I think she's given us all she can, or wants to. I will tell everyone to get ready to head out."
    Fa "Creo que nos ha dado todo lo que puede o quiere. Les diré a todos que se preparen para salir."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2456
translate spanish d8b76_fba987b4:

    # Fa "If you have more questions, they will have to wait until we hit the road."
    Fa "Si tienes más preguntas, tendrán que esperar hasta que nos pongamos en marcha."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2460
translate spanish d8b76_f7f6039b:

    # "Taking point on a small team headed by Fangs, you climb in your car and follow her indications towards the Hive."
    "Tomando como guía a un pequeño equipo encabezado por Fangs, subes a tu coche y sigues sus indicaciones hacia la Colmena."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2464
translate spanish d8b76_e173c614:

    # Fa "You didn't really think that a military base stuck in the middle of the desert wouldn't come equipped with several vehicles, did you?!"
    Fa "No pensarías realmente que una base militar metida en medio del Desierto no vendría equipada con varios vehículos, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2465
translate spanish d8b76_a6e5402b:

    # Z "And there I was thinking my new ride was a lucky find."
    Z "Y ahí estaba yo pensando que mi nuevo viaje era un hallazgo afortunado."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2466
translate spanish d8b76_1c982592:

    # Fa "Don't beat yourself up over it. It was a lucky find, and it's a good ride."
    Fa "No te castigues por ello. Fue un hallazgo afortunado y es un buen paseo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2469
translate spanish d8b76_294d49eb:

    # To "So, what do you say, ten more minutes until we get to this place? Twenty?"
    To "Entonces, ¿qué te parece, diez minutos más hasta que lleguemos a este lugar? ¿Veinte?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2470
translate spanish d8b76_ec01d2b0:

    # Re "Not to bug you, Pepper, but I'm curious as well."
    Re "No es por molestarte, Pepper, pero yo también tengo curiosidad."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2473
translate spanish d8b76_c703c2ce:

    # Re "I'm getting tired of driving, you know."
    Re "Me estoy cansando de conducir, ¿sabes?"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2476
translate spanish d8b76_e676adae:

    # Pe "Not unreasonable, you long for the adrenaline rush that comes with reaching the destination and facing the unknown. Driving becomes boring, after a while."
    Pe "No es descabellado, anhelas el subidón de adrenalina que supone llegar al destino y enfrentarte a lo desconocido. Conducir se vuelve aburrido, después de un tiempo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2479
translate spanish d8b76_8f9d5649:

    # Pe "Even so, please, do try to keep your eyes on the compass, rather than on the backseat of your car."
    Pe "Aun así, por favor, intenta mantener tus ojos en la brújula, en lugar de en el asiento trasero de tu coche."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2480
translate spanish d8b76_c4abfde6:

    # Pe "As for you, Towser... Stop staring, and maybe next time find yourself a hat, instead of a fancy mouth scarf. you are 70%% more likely to get a sunstroke this way."
    Pe "En cuanto a ti, Towser... Deja de mirar, y quizás la próxima vez búscate un sombrero, en lugar de un elegante pañuelo para la boca. tienes un 70%% más de probabilidades de sufrir una insolación de esta manera.."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2483
translate spanish d8b76_2e3987c0:

    # Pe "..."
    Pe "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2486
translate spanish d8b76_22375a79:

    # Pe "Stop trying to think about a retort. It makes your eyes twitch."
    Pe "Deja de pensar en una respuesta. Hace que tus ojos se muevan."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2489
translate spanish d8b76_5ddf044b:

    # To "..."
    To "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2490
translate spanish d8b76_a082f4f6:

    # To "{i}*sighs*"
    To "{i}*suspiros*"

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2493
translate spanish d8b76_8af0276a:

    # Fa "So... long story short, one of my girls found her strolling around, barely clothed, lost like a mummy in quicksand."
    Fa "Así que... resumiendo, una de mis chicas la encontró paseando, apenas vestida, perdida como una momia en arenas movedizas."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2494
translate spanish d8b76_efd3af7f:

    # Fa "She refused to say a word, even when she was brought to us."
    Fa "Se negó a decir una palabra, incluso cuando nos la trajeron."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2495
translate spanish d8b76_68557ce0:

    # Fa "After a day or so, she finally decided to speak."
    Fa "Después de un día o más, por fin se decidió a hablar."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2496
translate spanish d8b76_324941de:

    # Fa "Her voice was... A surprise, even for the likes of us."
    Fa "Su voz fue... Una sorpresa, incluso para los que son como nosotros."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2499
translate spanish d8b76_ba2611cf:

    # Fa "She told us the same things she told you earlier."
    Fa "Nos dijo lo mismo que te dijo a ti antes."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2500
translate spanish d8b76_9f7e0367:

    # Fa "I still have no idea what she means with that whole darkness issue, but..."
    Fa "Todavía no tengo ni idea de lo que quiere decir con todo el tema de la oscuridad, pero..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2503
translate spanish d8b76_d22938a8:

    # Fa "...She seems reluctant to go, so I am convinced she's not trying to lure us into anything."
    Fa "... Ella parece reacia a ir, así que estoy convencido de que no está tratando de atraernos a nada."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2506
translate spanish d8b76_4f46912e:

    # Fa "So, we're going in armed, but the objective is to learn, to talk and if possible, negotiate an alliance."
    Fa "Así que vamos armados, pero el objetivo es aprender, hablar y si es posible, negociar una alianza."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2507
translate spanish d8b76_a2f36dad:

    # Fa "You said it, we need allies. Other mutants seem like a good ally to try and get."
    Fa "Tú lo has dicho, necesitamos aliados. Otros mutantes son un buen aliado para tratar de conseguirlo."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2510
translate spanish d8b76_93aab215:

    # Fa "If it serves the purpose of establishing an alliance or at least a dialogue, I am willing to hand over their missing girl."
    Fa "Si sirve para establecer una alianza o al menos un diálogo, estoy dispuesta a entregar a su chica desaparecida."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2513
translate spanish d8b76_c5027359:

    # Fa "But I'd rather not break my promise and find something to trade instead."
    Fa "Pero prefiero no romper mi promesa y encontrar algo con lo que comerciar."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2516
translate spanish d8b76_d3c264bc_1:

    # Mu "..."
    Mu "..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2519
translate spanish d8b76_c5d239f2:

    # Fa "Two of us will guard the cars."
    Fa "Dos de nosotros vigilaremos los coches."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2520
translate spanish d8b76_052a633f:

    # Fa "If things go bad, we are not going to stay a minute longer than we need to."
    Fa "Si las cosas van mal, no nos quedaremos ni un minuto más de lo necesario."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2524
translate spanish d8b76_a12bc9ee:

    # "You eventually arrive to what seems to be your destination. There's a lot of rubble, obvious remains of an ancient city, but only one building is still standing, tall and imposing."
    "Finalmente llegas a lo que parece ser tu destino. Hay un montón de escombros, restos evidentes de una antigua ciudad, pero sólo un edificio sigue en pie, alto e imponente."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2525
translate spanish d8b76_b55d498a:

    # "From outside, it reminds you of some of the buildings in Cairo, a museum maybe, or something of a religious nature."
    "Desde el exterior, recuerda a algunos edificios del Cairo, un museo tal vez, o algo de carácter religioso."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2526
translate spanish d8b76_227ba8b1:

    # "Fangs is telling two of her squad members to guard the vehicles and the perimeter, while the rest will be going inside."
    "Fangs indica a dos de sus miembros del escuadrón que vigilen los vehículos y el perímetro, mientras que el resto entrará."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2527
translate spanish d8b76_2c7b99a8:

    # "As you enter the building, you notice it is shrouded in darkness. Heavily tinted windows caked with decades of accumulated sand do nothing to illuminate the place."
    "Al entrar en el edificio, observas que está envuelto en la oscuridad. Los cristales fuertemente tintados y apelmazados por décadas de arena acumulada no contribuyen a iluminar el lugar."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2531
translate spanish d8b76_f97fd58b:

    # Fa "Fuck me, this place is huge."
    Fa "Que me jodan, este sitio es enorme."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2534
translate spanish d8b76_724c9f3b:

    # Fa "Stay close, we're going to check each of those alcoves, but we stay together."
    Fa "Permanece cerca, vamos a revisar cada una de esas habitaciones, pero permanecemos juntos."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2535
translate spanish d8b76_c2e4a1f1:

    # To "Uhm, Commander... with all due respect to your abilities..."
    To "Uhm, Comandante... con todo el respeto a tus habilidades..."

# game/scripts/day8.rpy:2536
translate spanish d8b76_6bc0a290:

    # To "...we can't see shit."
    To "... no podemos ver una mierda."

