translate spanish strings:

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:668
    old "\"She has not finished her training yet, which is why I have always have tried to restrain myself.\""
    new "\"Aún no ha terminado su formación, por lo que siempre he intentado contenerme.\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:668
    old "\"She's a pretty girl, but she should go her own way.\""
    new "\"Es una chica bonita, pero debería seguir su propio camino.\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:723
    old "\"Of course I am interested, but until today, we have focused on her training.\""
    new "\"Por supuesto que me interesa, pero hasta hoy nos hemos centrado en su entrenamiento.\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:723
    old "\"She will go her own way.\""
    new "\"Seguirá su propio camino.\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:737
    old "\"We will talk about it, eventually.\""
    new "\"Hablaremos de ello, al final.\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:737
    old "\"It's not what I want for her.\""
    new "\"No es lo que quiero para ella.\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:923
    old "\"What's wrong?\""
    new "\"¿Qué pasa?\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:923
    old "\"Can't sleep?\""
    new "\"¿No puedes dormir?\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:923
    old "\"Did I forget your bedtime story?\""
    new "\"¿He olvidado tu cuento para dormir?\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:1095
    old "\"I have always forced myself away from this.\""
    new "\"Siempre me he obligado a alejarme de esto.\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:1095
    old "\"You are beautiful.\""
    new "\"Eres hermosa.\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:1095
    old "Pull her towards you"
    new "Tira de ella hacia ti"

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:1184
    old "Caress her neck"
    new "Acaricia su cuello"

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:1184
    old "Join hands"
    new "Une las manos"

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:1236
    old "\"You were right, I didn't really listen.\""
    new "\"Tenías razón, no escuché realmente.\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:1236
    old "\"You're in trouble now.\""
    new "\"Ahora tienes problemas.\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:1725
    old "[S] is on her own now. I need to wait for her return before I can provide the Queen with an update."
    new "[S] está sola ahora. Necesito esperar su regreso antes de poder proporcionar a la Reina una actualización."

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:1728
    old "[S] is on her way to the Zone. I need to wait for her return to find out what those blueprints are all about."
    new "[S] está de camino a la Zona. Necesito esperar su regreso para averiguar de qué tratan esos planos."

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:1787
    old "\"I'm here to speak with Fangs.\""
    new "\"Estoy aquí para hablar con Fangs.\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:1787
    old "\"I didn't expect someone that cute when I heard that voice.\""
    new "\"No esperaba a alguien tan mona cuando escuché esa voz.\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:1787
    old "\"You are very unsettling.\""
    new "\"Eres muy inquietante.\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:1877
    old "It seems like Fangs has big plans for the mutants. They could potentially be a force to be reckoned with in the region."
    new "Parece que Fangs tiene grandes planes para los mutantes. Podrían convertirse en una fuerza a tener en cuenta en la región."

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:1957
    old "\"I will help your people as long as you swear not to start a conflict.\""
    new "\"Ayudaré a tu pueblo siempre que jures no iniciar un conflicto.\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:1957
    old "\"I came to give you a warning, but I cannot assist you any further.\""
    new "\"Vine a darte una advertencia, pero no puedo ayudarte más.\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:2014
    old "\"Maybe I am just the man {i}you{/i} need around here.\""
    new "\"Tal vez soy el hombre que {i}tú{/i} necesitas por aquí.\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:2014
    old "\"And what do I get in return for helping you out?\""
    new "\"¿Y qué obtengo a cambio de ayudarte?\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:2014
    old "\"Are you looking to pass on the command?\""
    new "\"¿Buscas pasar el mando?\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:2024
    old "Take her top off"
    new "Quítale el top"

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:2024
    old "Don't take it off"
    new "No se lo quites"

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:2090
    old "Take off her top"
    new "Quítale el top"

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:2769
    old "Tell her to stay"
    new "Dile que se quede"

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:2769
    old "Take her back to base"
    new "Llévala de vuelta a la base"

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:2838
    old "Exploring the Hive was a bust. We had to run for our lives and I have decided to take the Daughter with us. If we are going to fix this, we need her with us."
    new "Explorar la Colmena fue un fracaso. Tuvimos que huir para salvar nuestras vidas y he decidido llevarnos a la Hija con nosotros. Si vamos a arreglar esto, la necesitamos con nosotros."

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:3021
    old "\"You live and learn, right?\""
    new "\"Se vive y se aprende, ¿verdad?\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:3021
    old "\"And I didn't expect someone like you to dye her hair...\""
    new "\"Y no esperaba que alguien como tú se tiñera el pelo...\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:3060
    old "\"Alright then, do what you have to do.\""
    new "\"De acuerdo entonces, haz lo que tengas que hacer.\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:3060
    old "\"Let's stop. I didn't sign up for this.\""
    new "\"Dejémoslo. Yo no me apunté a esto.\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:3082
    old "Try to finish"
    new "Intenta terminar"

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:3082
    old "Convince her to take off her coat"
    new "Convéncela de que se quite la bata"

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:2865
    old "Exploring the Hive was a bust. We had to run for our lives and leave the Daughter behind. I think having her back will give us more credit with the Queen, when we try to contact her again."
    new "Explorar la colmena fue un fracaso. Tuvimos que huir para salvar nuestras vidas y dejar atrás a la Hija. Creo que recuperarla nos dará más crédito ante la Reina cuando intentemos contactar con ella de nuevo."

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:3334
    old "\"If you're here to sample my wife's cooking...\""
    new "\"Si estás aquí para probar la cocina de mi mujer...\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:3334
    old "\"You're going to disappear again, aren't you?\""
    new "\"Vas a desaparecer de nuevo, ¿verdad?\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:3409
    old "\"I didn't expect you to speak.\""
    new "\"No esperaba que hablaras.\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:3409
    old "\"What are you thanking me for?\""
    new "\"¿Por qué me das las gracias?\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:3409
    old "\"Does Fangs need my help again?\""
    new "\"¿Vuelve a necesitar Fangs mi ayuda?\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:3445
    old "\"I don't agree with how your kind are treated.\""
    new "\"No estoy de acuerdo con el trato que reciben los de tu especie.\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:3445
    old "\"No one deserves to end up like that.\""
    new "\"Nadie merece acabar así.\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:3445
    old "\"You got yourself into a tight spot.\""
    new "\"Te metiste en un lío.\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:3529
    old "\"See you soon, Ivy. \""
    new "\"Hasta pronto, Ivy.\""

    # game/scripts/day8.rpy:3529
    old "\"Your friend?\""
    new "\"¿Tu amiga?\""



